\id JHN  
\h John 
\toc1 John Sut Kipana Thupha 
\toc2 John 
\toc3 Jn 
\mt1 JOHN  
\mt2 KIPANA THUPHA  
\mt3 Natahsan theina ding'un  
\is1 Jesu Pathen Chapa tahbeh, thutah le ngailutna bulhingset a kiphong doh  
\is1 Gospel John lekhabu sung thu umdan  
\ip John lekhabu hi Jesu natoh jatchom chom chule ipi jeh pen'a hung ham ti bailam tah a hetna hi ding ahi. John in aseibena ah, Jesun thilphabep kultah a ngaito dingin natoh anei e, hiche natoh phabep akon chun Ama koi ahi, hetdohna tei ding ahi. Jesun melchihna sagi abol ho bou John in ajihlut ahi. Ajeh chu hiche melchihna ho hin Jesu Pathen Chapa ahi, ti aphochen in ahi. John in aseijin, “Vannoi pumpi lekhabu kijih ho sanga hop-lenjo ahi,” ati \xt Jn 21:25\xt*. Ipi dinga melchihna hichengse hi alhendoh ham? Ajeh chu tahsanna dihtah nei ding, “Jesu Messiah le Pathen Chapa ahi ti, tahsan jingna ding le tahsan jal'a Ama min'a hinna nei theina ding ahi,” \xt Jn 20:31\xt*.  
\ip Gospel John hin, Vah chule Hinna hi Pathen natoh ho hinkho lamhil'a pang ahi, ti avetsah e. Jesu thuhil chom chom gospel danga kimulou jong ajaovin ahi. Jesu Meissiah, Van'a kon Hinna Changlhah, Pathen hinsol, Vannoi vah, Kot, Kelngoi ching, Pathen Chapa, Thodoh kitna, Hinna, Lampi, Thutah, Lengpigui tahbeh chule Judah te lengpa ahi. Hiche hoa kon tahsanna dihtah neina ding tina ahi.  
\is1 Lekhabu jihpa chule ajih kum  
\ip Solchah John, Zebedee chapa \xt Mk 1:19\xt*, Jesu seijui som le ni lah a alailah pen, ngailut John tia jong kihepa sut ahi. Alhangpi pomdan in AD 80-95 sunga asut hi dingin tahsan ahi. Chule Ephesus khopi, tukhanga Turkey, aum sunga anajih ahi.  
\is1 Koi henga chule ipi dinga ajih ham?  
\ip Asia minor gamsunga Judah mi hilou, Jesu tahsan a anungjui ho gelkhohna a ajih ahi. Amaho chu alhangpia Greek miho chihgilna thuhil hatna mun'a cheng ho ahiuve. Chulaiya Greek te thuhil loupi khat chu, Jesu chu Pathen ahin, mihem tahbeh ahipoi tia hetchenna giltah neiho bou huhhingna chang ahi, atiuve. Hijeh chun John in, “Huhhingna chu Pathen Chapa Jesu eiho lhatdoh dinga mihem tahsaphe a hung ahi, ti tahsan jouse chang ding ahi,” ati.  
\c 1  
\s1 Thu chu mihem ahung sohtai  
\p
\v 1 Thu chu atil abul'a ana umsa ahi. Thu chu Pathen toh umkhom ahin, chule Thu chu Pathen ahi.  
\v 2 Ama chu atil abul'a Pathen toh umkhomsa ahi.  
\v 3 Pathen'in amavang a thil jouse anasem ahin, chule Ama louva kisem doh khatcha jong aumpoi.  
\v 4 Thu chun thil jouse hinna apeh ahin, chule Ama hinna chun amichang cheh vah apeh ahitai.  
\v 5 Vah chun muthim lah ahinsal in, chule muthin'in vah chu asumit joupoi.  
\v 6 Pathen'in mikhat, Twilutsah John ahin sol'in,\x + \xo 1:6 \xt Matt 3:1; Mk 1:4; Lk 3:1,2\x*  
\v 7 aman vah thu a hettohsah chu ama thuseiya konna amichang cheh in atahsan theina dingu ahi.  
\v 8 John ama tah chu vah ahipoi, vah thudol hettohsah a seiphong chu ahije.  
\v 9 Vannoiya hunga, amichang cheh vah hung pea, Ama bou chu vah tahbeh ahi.  
\v 10 Asemsa vannoiya ama ana hungin, hinla vannoiyin ama ahedoh pouve.  
\v 11 Ama amite henga anahung chun, amiten ama ana sang tapouve.  
\v 12 Ahivangin koi hileh ama tahsan le ama kisa'n jouse chu Pathen chate hitheina thuneina apetai.  
\v 13 Amaho penthah chu tahsa pen ngai'a mihem lung lam'a konna tahsa lunggon'a penga ahipouvin, Pathen'a kon peng'a ahibou uve.  
\v 14 Hiti hin Thu chu tahsapu mihem ahung kisoh in, chule ilah uva ahung chengtai. Ama lhadahlou ngailut le kitahna dimset ahin, keihon ama loupina, Pa Chapa changkhat seh ahina loupitah chu kamu tauve.  
\v 15 John chun Jesu thudol'a hettohsah in, mipi ho henga asam'in “Hiche pa hi ahi, athudol kana hettohsah chu, Kanunga mi khat ahungin, ama chu kei sanga gamchenga lenjo ahi, ajeh chu ama keima masang peh a anaumsa ahitai, kati chu,” ati.  
\v 16 Ama aning lhinsetna konna eiho jouse lungset vangbohna hi aban ban'a changa ihitauve.  
\v 17 Ijeh ham itileh danthu chu Mose a kon ahin, hinla lhadahlou Pathen mi ngailutna le kitahna chu Jesu Messiah vanga hungah ahi bouve.  
\v 18 Koima Pathen mukha ana umpoi. Ahin atepi umlou, ama tah Pathen Chapa changkhat seh, Pa lung to kinaicha um jing chun, eiho henga aphondoh ahitai.   
\s1 Twilutsah John hettohsah  
\p
\v 19 Hiche hi Juda te lamkai hon Jerusalem'a pat a thempu ho leh Hou-In a sottol leho, John henga “Nang koi nahim?” tia aga dohsah nauva, John in a hettohsah chu ahi.  
\v 20 Ama ahung kiphong doh paijin, “Keima Messiah kahipoi” ati jenge.  
\v 21 Chuphatnin ama hon adongun, “Achutile aphai, koi nahi ham? Nangma Elijah nahim?” atiuve. Aman adonbut in “Kahipoi” ati. “Ahile kaginchat u themgao chu nahim?” atiuve. Aman “Kahipoi” ati.\x + \xo 1:21 \xt Malachi 4:5; \xt Danbu Ni Na 18:15,18\x*  
\v 22 “Achutile koi nahim? Eihinsol ho kom'a lhut ding donbutna kangai chauve. Nangman koi kahi nakiti em?” atiuve.  
\v 23 John in adonbut in Keima gamthip a khosam awgin'in, “Pakai hungna ding lampi sutheng un,” tia Isaiah themgao thusei chu kahi, ati.\x + \xo 1:23 \xt Isa 40:3\x*  
\v 24 Hichun Pharisee ho ahung kisol ho chun,  
\v 25 Ama adong un, “Messiah nahi louva, Elijah nahi louva, chule themgao nahilou le, ipi thuneina naneiya Baptize nachan sah ham?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 26 Chuin John in amaho jah a, “Keiman twiya Baptize kachan sah ahin, ahinlah mipi lah a nang hon nahet dohlou u mikhat aum'e.  
\v 27 Ama keima nunga hung ahivangin keima ama soh dinga jong lhing joulou chule akengchot khao sutlham dinga jong kilom kahipoi,” ati.  
\v 28 Hicheng chu Jordan vadung gal solam Bethany mun'a John in Baptize achansahna a thilsoh ahi.   
\s1 Pathen kelngoinou  
\p
\v 29 Ajingin John in ama heng lam'a Jesu ahung amun, “Veuvin, vannoi chonset pomang Pathen kelngoinou khu,”  
\v 30 Ama hi ahi keiman kasei, kanunga hunga kei sanga gamchenga lenjo, kati chu, ajeh chu ama kei um masang peh a ana umsa ahitai, ati.  
\v 31 “Keiman ama Christa ahilam kana hepoi, ahivangin ama chu Israel lah a phondoh a aumna dinga keiman twiya Baptize kachan sah ahi,” ati.  
\v 32 Chuin John in athu hettohsah nan, “Keiman van'a kon'a Lhagao Theng vakhu banga ahung lenlhah a achunga aumden kamui.”  
\v 33 Keiman ama ahilam kana hepoi, ahivang'in Pathen'in twiya Baptize chan sah dinga eisol chun, aman kakom'a “Achunga Lhagao Theng achuh a aumden namupa chun, Lhagao Thenga baptize ahin chan sah ding ahi,”  
\v 34 “Chule keiman Jesu chunga hicheng asopet hi kamun, hijeh a chu ama hi Pathen'in alhendoh achapa khat seh chu ahi tia ka hettohsah ahitai,” ati.  
\v 35 Ajing kit in, John aseijui mini toh adinpet un,  
\v 36 Jesun ahinjotpa chu amun, ama chu aven, “Veuvin Pathen kelngoinou khu,” ati.   
\s1 Seijui masa ho  
\p
\v 37 Chuin John seijui teni chun athusei chu ajalhonin, Jesu nung ajuilhon tai.  
\v 38 Chuin Jesu akihei leh amanin ajuilhon chu amun, “Ipi na ngaichat lhon ham?” atitai. Amanin adonbut lhon'in “Rabbi” (Hichu houhil tina ahi) hoiya na umji ham? atilhon e.  
\v 39 Chuin aman, “Hung lhonin hungve lhonin,” ati. Amani Jesu toh akilhon khom lhonin, aumna chu aga mulhon tai. Chule hiche nikho chun aumkhom tauve. Hichu nilhangkai nidan li don ahi.  
\v 40 John thuseiya, Jesu nungjui teni lah a khat joh chu, Simon Peter naopa Andrew chu ahi.  
\v 41 Andrew chun asopipa Simon aga holdoh in ajah a, “Keihon Messiah (Christa tina ahi) kamu tauve,” ati.  
\v 42 Chuin Andrew in Simon chu Jesu henga ahinpuiyin ahi. Hichun Jesun Simon chu aven ajah a, “Nangma John chapa Simon nahi, hijongleh Cephas kisah ding nahitai. (Hichu Peter tina ahi).”  
\v 43 Ajingin Jesu Galilee lam'a che dingin aum'e. Hichun aman Philip amun, ajah a “Hungin neijuijin,” ati.  
\v 44 Philip chu Andrew leh Peter chenna khopi Bethsaida kho a kon ahi.  
\v 45 Chuin Philip in Nathanael aholdoh in ajah a, “Mose le themgao hon athudol anasut u amapa tah chu kamu tauve. Ama chu Nazareth khomi, Joseph chapa, Jesu ahi,” ati.  
\v 46 Hichun Nathanael in adatmo lheh in, “Nazareth khoa kon'a thilpha sohdoh thei hinam?” ati. Philip in adonbut in “Hungin nangma tah in hungven” ati.  
\v 47 Akom lhon'a amani ahung lhon chu Jesun amun, ajah lhon'a, “Phatlhemna beihel mikitahpa, Israel chapa dihtah chu tun aumtai,” ati.  
\v 48 Nathenael in adongin, “Iti neihet jeng ham?” ati. Jesun adonbut in, “Philip in naholdoh masanga theichang phung noiya na umpet a chu kamu nahitai,” ati.  
\v 49 Chuin Nathanael tijatah in, “Rabbi nangma Pathen Chapa, Israel te lengpa nahi,” tin aphongtai.  
\v 50 Chuin Jesun adongin, “Theichang phung noiya na umpet kamu ahitai, kati jeh a chu na tahsan ham? Hiche sanga chungnungjo namu ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 51 Chujouvin ama jah a, “Atahbeh ka seipeh nahi, nangman van akihon'a chule Pathen vantil ho Mihem Chapa chunga akaltou le akumsuh namu ding ahi, ajeh chu ama tah chu van le lei kimatna kalbilei ahi,” ati.   
\c 2  
\s1 Cana kho a moupui golvah  
\p
\v 1 Ajingin Galilee gamsunga Cana khoa kichenna golvah kin khat aumin ahi. Chua chun Jesu nu jong aumin,  
\v 2 Chule hiche kin a chu Jesu leh aseijui ho jong akouvu ahi.  
\v 3 Golvahna aum petnin lengpitwi alhing tahih in, anu chun Jesu jah a “Lengpitwi anei tapouve,” ati.  
\v 4 “Ngailut umtah numei, hichu eiho boipi ding ahipoi” tia Jesun adonbut ahi. “Keima phat lhing loulai hichu,” ati.  
\v 5 Ahivangin anu chun lhacha ho jah a, “Aman najah uva asei ipi hijongleh bol un,” ati.  
\v 6 Akom tah uva chun Juda te dan dungjuiya kisuhtheng na songbel lentah gup uma ahi. Bel khat chu twi-thei dim somni apat somthum dol cheh ahi.  
\v 7 Jesun soh ho jah a “Songbel ho chu twi sung dimun,” ati. Ama hon songbel ho chu twi asun dim phatnun,  
\v 8 Aman ajah uva, “Tun phabep thaldoh unlang golvah vaihompa henga choiyun,” ati. Hiti chun lhacha ho chun athupeh bang chun abol tauve.  
\v 9 Golvah vaihompa chun, twisih lengpitwi kisosah chu ate khah phatnin, ahung kondohna hechen louvin (Lhacha hon vang aheuve), moulang chu akoutai.  
\v 10 Aman ajah a, “Kinbol'a chun lengpitwi chihpen ahomdoh masa jin, mihon adon khop tengleh, adaojep ahomji bouve. Ahin nangman tugeiyin achih pen nahom nalaiye!” ati.  
\v 11 Galilee gam'a Cana khoa hiche melchihna kidang abol hi ama loupi kiphondohna dinga anatoh masapen ahi. Chuin aseijui ten ama atahsan tauve.  
\v 12 Kichenna golvah kichai jin, ama le anu toh, asopiho toh, chule aseijui ho toh Capernaum a nikho phabep din ache tauvin ahi.\x + \xo 2:12 \xt Matt 4:13\x*   
\s1 Jesun Hou-In asuhtheng  
\p
\v 13 Chuin Judah te Kalchuh Kut anai phat in, Jesu Jerusalem'a achetai.\x + \xo 2:13 \xt Potdohbu 12:1-27\x*  
\v 14 Hou-In sunga chun aman kivei mihon kilhaina thilto ding bongho, kelngoiho chule vapal ho ajoh uva chuleh sum lhengho atouvu amudoh tai.  
\v 15 Hichun Jesun khao phabep a jepna ding asemin, amaho jouse chu Hou-In a kon'in adeldoh in, chule aman bongho le kelngoiho anodoh in, sum lhengho sumnong chu athethang peh in chule adokhangu alekhup pehtai.  
\v 16 Chuin, vapal joh ho kom'a achen ajah uva, “Hiche ho hi hilai mun'a kon'in podoh un. Kapa In chu nang hon kailhang mun sosah hih un!” ati.  
\v 17 Hichun aseijui ten, Pathen Lekhabua themgao thusei, “Na-In dinga katompan hin katha jouse eine chaiye,” tichu ahin geldoh tauve.\x + \xo 2:17 \xt Labu 69:9\x*  
\v 18 Ahivangin Judah vaipo hon ajah a “Ipi ham nabol? Hitobang bolna dinga thuneina Pathen'in napeh mong ahileh amelchihna kidang khat nei musah un,” atiuve.  
\v 19 Jesun adonbut in, “Aphai, hiche Hou-In hi suchim un, chule Keiman nithum in tungdoh inge,” ati.\x + \xo 2:19 \xt Matt 26:61; 27:40; Mk 14:58; 15:29\x*  
\v 20 Hichun amaho tijatah in, “Hiche Hou-In sahna a kum som li le kum gup jen lut a, nangin nithum'a iti nasah doh ding ong?” atiuve.  
\v 21 Ahivangin, Jesun hiche Hou-In ati chu Ama tahsa aseina ahi bouve.  
\v 22 Hiche hi Ama thina a konna kaithouva aum nung chun, aseijui ten ipi aseina ahi ahin geldoh un, Pathen Lekhabua thu ho leh Jesu thusei ho atahsan tauve.  
\v 23 Kalchuh Kut laiya, Jerusalem'a aumpet a Jesun thil kidang melchihna abol ho jeh chun mi tamtah in ama atahsan tauve.  
\v 24 Ahivangin amaho chu Jesun atahsan poi, ajeh chu mihem hina chu aman ahetsa ahi.  
\v 25 Ama dingin mikhat thudol adang khat in ama henga hettohsah angaipoi, ajeh chu mijouse lungsung ahetsa ahi.   
\c 3  
\s1 Jesu le Nicodemus  
\p
\v 1 Pharisee mi amin Nicodemus kiti Judah te hou lamkai khat aum'e.  
\v 2 Amapa chu jankhat Jesu henga ahungin Jesu jah a, “Houhil, keiho dinga Pathen'in nahin sol ahi kaheuve; melchihna kidang hijat nabol ho hi Pathen'a kon nahi aphotchetna ahitai,” ati.  
\v 3 Jesun adonbut in “Tahbeh a ka seipeh nahi, nangma napen kit louleh Pathen Lenggam namu louding ahi,” ati.  
\v 4 Nicodemus chun datmo tah in, “Mi ateh nunga iti anu naobu a lelut kit a hung pengkit thei ding ham?” ati.  
\v 5 Jesun adonbut in, “Thutah chu ahileh, twiya le lhagaova apenlou le koima Pathen Lenggam alut theipoi.  
\v 6 Mihem tahsaphe a penga chu tahsa a hinna bou ahin, ahivangin Lhagao Thenga penga chu Lhagaova hinna chang ahi.  
\v 7 Hijeh chun 'nangma napen kit ding ahi,' kati chu datmo hih in.  
\v 8 Hui khu anopna lam lam'a anungin, nangin agin najan, ahivangin hoiya hungkon hoilam ajot nahepoi, chutobang chun Lhagaova pengho jong nangin nahe theipoi,” ati.  
\v 9 Chuin Nicodemus chun ajah a “Hiche ho chu iti hithei ding ham?” ati.  
\v 10 Jesun adonbut in, “Nangla Judah te houhil pipu khat nahin, hiche ho hi iti nahet theilou ham?  
\v 11 Tahbeh a ka seipeh nahi, keihon kahet kaseiyu ahin, kamu ka hettohsah u ahi; ahivangin ka hettohsah uhi nang hon nasang pouve.  
\v 12 Keiman leiset thil ho kaseiya na tahsan louleh, van'a thil ho thudol seileng iti na tahsan ding ham?  
\v 13 Koima van'a akal'in, ahung kile khapoi; ahivangin Mihem Chapa vang chu van'a konna hung kumlha ahi.  
\v 14 Chuleh Mose in gamthip a thing'a sum-eng gul adop sang banga chu, Mihem Chapa kidom sang ding,\x + \xo 3:14 \xt Minbu 21:9\x*  
\v 15 hijeh chun amitakip ama tahsan chan in tonsot hinna anei ding ahi.”  
\v 16 “Ajeh chu Pathen'in hibanga hi vannoi angailut ahin: Koi hijongleh Ama tahsan chan chu mangthah louva tonsot hinna aneina dingin, aneisun achapa changkhat chu apetan ahi.  
\v 17 Pathen'in achapa vannoiya ahinsol chu, vannoi huhhing'a aumna ding joh ahi bouve.”  
\v 18 “Koi hileh ama tahsan chan chu, achunga thutanna umlou ahitai; ahivangin koi hijongleh atahsanlou vang chu, Pathen chapa changkhat chu atahsan loujeh a achunga thutanna umsa ahitai.  
\v 19 Chule thutanna chu hiche hi ahi; Pathen vah chu vannoiya ahungin, ahivangin mihon vah sangin, achonna u aphatlou jeh in muthim joh adeijouvin ahi.  
\v 20 Michonphalou jousen vah athet un, nai jong anailut ngam pouve, ajeh chu achonset nau hin phongdoh khante tin akichauve.  
\v 21 Ahivangin thudih a chonphat bol ho vang chun Pathen lungdei abol'u chu mihon amutheina dingin vah a aum jing uve.”   
\s1 Twilutsah John in Jesu achoisang  
\p
\v 22 Chuin Jesu leh seijui ten Jerusalem adalhauvin, Judea gam thinglhang lam ajon tauve; chukom'a chun phat chomkhat aumkhom'un, miho baptize achansah jin ahi.  
\v 23 Hiche pet chun Twilutsah John injong Salim kom'a Aenon mun'a twi ninglhing tah a aum jeh chun, miho baptize achansah jin, chule aphat seh in, miho jong baptize chang dingin ahung jingun ahi.  
\v 24 Hichu John songkul'a akikhum masang ahi.\x + \xo 3:24 \xt Matt 14:3; Mk 6:17; Lk 3:19,20\x*  
\v 25 Hichun kisuhthengna thudol'a John seijui ho leh Judah mi phabep kikah a kinelna anasoh in ahi.  
\v 26 Hijeh chun John seijui ho ahenga ahung'un, ajah a “Rabbi (hichu houhil tina ahi), Jordan luigala nakimupi a ama Messiah ahi tia na hettohsah pa jong chun miho baptize achansah jin ahi. Chuleh mi tampi eiho henga hung talouvin ama henga ache tauve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 27 Chuin John in adonbut in “Pathen'in van'a konna apehlou chu, koima ima achang theipoi.  
\v 28 Keiman naheng uva kasei chu, nangho ahetoh ah nahiuve; keima Christa kahipoi, ama lampi semtoh dinga hung kahi bouve.\x + \xo 3:28 \xt Jn 1:20\x*  
\v 29 Hiche hi ahi, mou kichenpia chu moulang ahin; chuleh moulang jolpa vang chu moulang kom'a adin'a moulang kitepna ajah chu akipana ahijenge. Hijeh chun ama lolhinna chun keima kipana dim'a eikoi ahi.  
\v 30 Ama chu khangtou touding, chule keima kemsuh suh ding kahi.   
\s1 Van'a hungkon Jesu  
\p
\v 31 Ama chunga hungkon ahin, mijouse sanga chungnungjo ahi; Eiho leiset a kon ihiuvin, leiset thu iseiyu ahi, ahivangin ama chu chunga kon ahijeh in mijouse chunga achungnungpen ahi.  
\v 32 Aman amu leh ajah chu a hettohsah ahi, ahivangin ama hettohsah chu koiman asangpoi.  
\v 33 Hijeh chun koi hileh, athu hettohsah tahsan'a kisan chun Pathen dihtah chu apomdet ahitai.  
\v 34 Ama chu Pathen hinsol ahi, Aman Pathen thutah aseiye, ajeh chu ama Pathen Lhagao dimset a kipe ahi.  
\v 35 Pa chun Achapa angailun, chule ima jouse ama khut a apetai.\x + \xo 3:35 \xt Matt 11:27; Lk 10:22\x*  
\v 36 Hijeh chun, koi hijongleh Pathen tahsan'a chun tonsot hinna anei ahitai. Pathen chapa thungailou vang chu tonsot hinna chang louva Pathen lunghanna thutan chu achunga chu ding ahi,” ati.   
\c 4  
\s1 Jesu leh Samaria numeinu  
\p
\v 1 Pakai chun John sangin seijui tamjo asem'in miho Baptize achansah jinge ti Pharisee hon aja tauve tichu Jesun ahetan ahi.  
\v 2 Hichun Jesu ama tah in baptize achansah lou vang'in, aseijui ten abol'u ahi.  
\v 3 Hijeh chun aman Judea gam adalhan Galilee gam'a akile tai.  
\v 4 Aman alampi'a chun Samaria gamsung ajotpa in;  
\v 5 Chuti chun Samaria mite khokhat Sychar mun chu ahunglhung tai; hiche mun chu Jacob in achapa Joseph ana peh loumun kom ahi.\x + \xo 4:5 \xt Semtilbu 33:19; Joshua 24:32\x*  
\v 6 Chukom'a chu Jacob twikul um'ah ahi, Jesu chu lamsao ajotna'ah achol tan, twikul panga chun leltah in atouvin ahi; Hichu sunkim dontah ahi.  
\v 7 Hichun Samaria numei khat twithal dingin ahungin, Jesun amanu jah a “Lungset tah in twi don ding neipen” ati.  
\v 8 Hiche pet a chu Jesu achangseh a bou um ahi, ajeh chu aseijui te khosunga anneh ding choa achedoh kah u ahi.  
\v 9 Numeinu chu atija lheh e, ajeh chu Judah hon Samaria miho chu athet uva imacha akikoppi ngailou u ahi; hijeh chun amanun Jesu jah a “Nangla Judah mi nahin, keila Samaria numei kahin, ipi dinga keikom'a don ding twi nathum ham?” ati.\x + \xo 4:9 \xt Ezra 4:1-5; Nehemiah 4:1,2\x*  
\v 10 Jesun adonbut in amanu jah a “Pathen thilpeh nachan ding hi henlang, chule naki houpi hi koi ahi hele chun nangin kei kom'a nathum joh ding, chule keiman nangma hintwi pedinga,” ati.  
\v 11 Chuin amanun ajah a, “Pu nangman athaldohna ding khao le bel jong nei louva, twikul jong athuh in, hintwi nati chu hoiya nalah ding ham?  
\v 12 Chukit jongleh hiche twikul eina peuva kapului u Jacob sang'a nangma chungnungjo nahim? Ama tah in ana don'a achate leh agancha ho ana donsah a hiche twi sanga phajo hoiya nalah ding ham?” ati.  
\v 13 Jesun adonbut in ajah a, “Koi hileh hiche twi don'a chu dangchah kit ding ahi.  
\v 14 Ahivangin Keiman kapeh ding twi don jouse chu a itih a dangchah kit louding, amaho chu asung uva hintwi put a twinah theng soh ding, chule tonsot hinna chang ding ahiuve.”  
\v 15 Chuin numeinun ajah a “Pu lungset in hiche twi chu kei neipen, chuteng avel'a ka dangchah kitlouna ding, chuleh hilai mun'a twithal'a kahungkit louna dingin,” ati.  
\v 16 Chuin Jesun amanu jah a, “Chenlang najipa gakouvin,” ati.  
\v 17 Amanun adonbut in, “Keiman ji kaneipoi,” ati, hichun Jesun ajah a, “Nasei dih e, nangman ji kicheh naneipoi____  
\v 18 nangman ji nga tah nanei tan chule tua naum khompi pa jong khu naji tah ahipoi, nasei dih lheh jenge!” ati.  
\v 19 Chuin numeinun ajah a, “Pu,” “Nangma themgao khat nahi.”  
\v 20 Ahile neisei peh in, ipi dinga keiho Samaria mihon, kapului teu bolbanga hiche Gerizim mol'a Pathen kahou uva, ahivanga nangho Judah mihon Pathen houna ding mun chu Jerusalem bou ahi, natiu ham?” ati.  
\v 21 Jesun adonbut in, “Numei, nei tahsan in, nang hon Pathen nahouna dingu mun chu hiche mol'a jong hilou, chuleh Jerusalem'a jong hilou, phat chu ahunglhung e.  
\v 22 Nangho Samaria mihon nahet chen lou u nahouvun, ahivangin keiho Judah mihon vang kahou u ama chu kahet chen'u ahi; ajeh chu huhhingna chu Judah te a konna hung ahi bouve.  
\v 23 Ahivangin phat chu ahung lhunge, tutah hi ahi, ahou tahbeh hon Pa chu Lhagao leh thutah a ahou ding phat; ajeh chu Pa chun chutobanga hou ho bou chu amahou dinga ahol ahi.  
\v 24 Ajeh chu “Pathen chu lhagao ahin, ahouten lhagao leh thutah a ahou ding mong ahi,” ati.  
\v 25 Chuin numeinun ajah a, “Keiman Messiah hung ding chu kahenai, ama chu Christa ahi. Ama chu ahung tengleh aman ijakai eihil dingu ahi,” ati.  
\v 26 Chuin Jesun amanu jah a, “Keima Messiah chu kahi!” ati.  
\v 27 Hiche pettah chun, aseijui te ahung kile tauve, ama hon Jesu leh numeinu kihou chu amu uvin, atija lheh jengun ahi, ahivangin koiman ajah a, “Amanu henga ipi nathum ham?” ahilouleh, “Ipi dinga amanu naki houpi ham?” tia dong ngam aum pouve.  
\v 28 Hichun numeinu chun a twibel chu twikul panga adalhan khosung lam'a ale lhai kit in miho jouse henga;  
\v 29 “Hungun mikhat hung veuvin, aman kathilbol leh kachonna jouse aseidoh sohkeiye, Ama hi Christa hitei yinte,” ati.  
\v 30 Chuin khosunga kon chun mipi tamtah ahung potdoh un ama chu ahung veuvin ahi.  
\v 31 Hiche pet chun aseijui ten Jesu heng'ah, “Rabbi an themkhat beh nen,” atiuve.  
\v 32 Ahivangin Jesun adonbut in, “Keiman nangho het phahlou anneh kaneiye,” ati.  
\v 33 Hichun aseijui te amaho akidong touvin, “Eiho chedoh kah a mikhat touvin anneh ding ahin choipeh khat ham?” atiuve.  
\v 34 Chuin Jesun ahilchen in ajah uva, “Eisolpa Pathen lunggot lam bol leh akin suh bulhit chu keima anneh ahi,” ati.  
\v 35 “Nanghon changphu apat chang-at khomna ding lha li alut e' natiuvin ahi. Ahivangin keiman najah uva kasei ahi, khodah uvin loujao khu veuvin, chang amin'in a-atphat val ahitai.  
\v 36 Chang-at chun athaman akisanji mong ahi, chule a-atkhom lousohga chu miho tonsot hinna a apuilut chu ahi; chutia chu aphut pa le a atpa anilhon'a kipahkhomji ahi!  
\v 37 Akiseiji bang chun, ‘mikhat in aphut in adang khat in a-at khomji,’ kiti chu adihtah ahi.  
\v 38 Hijeh chun keiman nangho, na phulou nauva a-atkhom dinga kasol nahiuve; midang in atoh gimnasa chu nang hon aga nakhop tup u ahi.”   
\s1 Samaria Mihon Jesu Atahsan'u  
\p
\v 39 Numeinu chun, “Kathilbol leh kachonna jouse eiseidoh peh e,” tia a hettohsah a kon chun, chuche khoa Samaria mi tamtah in Jesu chu atahsan tauve.  
\v 40 Chuin amaho Jesu henga ahung'un, akom uva umden dingin a ngeh un ahi, chuin Jesu chukom'a chun nikho ni achongden tan ahi;  
\v 41 Chua aum sung chun mi tamtah in athusei ajah uva kon chun ama chu atahsan tauve.  
\v 42 Chuin ama hon numeinu jah a, “Nangma thu hettohsah jengseh hilouvin, keiho tah in ama thusei kajauvin, tun katahsan tauve, chuleh ama hi vannoi huhhing dihtah ahi kahechen tauve,” atiuvin ahi.   
\s1 Galilee mihon Jesu asan u  
\p
\v 43 Chua ni ni achon jou chun, Jesun Galilee ajontai.  
\v 44 Jesu ama tah in themgao chu achenna agamsung'a jabolna achangpoi, tia ana seidohsa ahi.\x + \xo 4:44 \xt Matt 13:57; Mk 6:4; Lk 4:24\x*  
\v 45 Ahijeng vang chun Galilee miten ama chu ana sang uve, ajeh chu amaho chu Kalchuh Kut laiya Jerusalem'a ana um uva, chumun'a Jesu thilbol ho ana musoh keiyu ahi.\x + \xo 4:45 \xt Jn 2:23\x*  
\v 46 Aman Galilee gamsung ajot in twisih lengpitwi asosah na Cana khoa chun ache kit in ahi, chuche kho kom'a Capernaum kho a chun vaipo milal khat aum'in, achapa chu ha dammo lheh jeng ahi.\x + \xo 4:46 \xt Jn 2:1-11\x*  
\v 47 Chuin aman Jesu chu Judea gam'a kon'in Galilee gam'a ahunge ti ajah phat in, ama tah Jesu henga achen, Capernaum geiya ahunga achapa ahung damsah dingin ataotai, ajeh chu achapa chu athikon cha ahitai.  
\v 48 Jesun ajah a, “Melchihna kidang hicheng ho hi mulou hile chun nei tahsan nadem?” ati.  
\v 49 Hichun vaipopa chun, “Pakai lungset in kachapa athi masangin hungin,” tin ataotai.  
\v 50 Jesun amapa jah a, “Na in'ah kile tan nachapa ahinge!” ati. Chuin mipa chun, Jesu thusei chu atahsan in, a inlam ajontai.  
\v 51 Chuin mipa chu a in alhun masang'in, asohten lampia ahung lamtouvin, achapa damtheng thu chu ahung seipeh uvin ahi.  
\v 52 Hichun aman asohte jah a, “Itih phat a chu damdoh ham?” tin adongin ahileh, ama hon, “Jan hi sun nidan khat dontah chun akhosih abeitai,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 53 Chuin mipa chun hiche phat laitah chu, Jesun ajah a 'na chapa ahinge' tia aseipet tah ahi chu ahedoh tan ahi; hiche jeh chun ama leh a Insung mite chengsen Jesu atahsan tauve.  
\v 54 Hiche hi Judea gam'a kon'a Galilee gam'a ahungna a Jesun melchihna kidang abol aniveina ahitai.   
\c 5  
\s1 Bethsaida twikul a nakong chatmopa  
\p
\v 1 Hiche jou chun, Judah ho kut nikho thengho jeh in Jesu chu Jerusalem'a akile kit in ahi.  
\v 2 Khopi sunglam'a kelngoi kotphung kom'a chun, Bethsaida kiti twikul khat aum'in akimvel'a chu leibuh nga kisa ahi.  
\v 3 Hiche mun'a chu ana damlou mitcho, elbai, langthi, chatmo tampi lum ahiuve, ajeh chu twi kicholing ngah jing'a um ahiuve.  
\v 4 Ajeh chu phat khat kom kom leh Pakai Vantil hung kumlha jia, twi chu acholing ji ahi; chuleh twi kicholoh nung'a twilah a kumlha masapen pen chu itobang natna hijongleh damhel ji ahi.  
\v 5 Hilai mun'a umho lah a mikhat chu kum somthum leh kum get jen nakong chatmo a lum ahitai.  
\v 6 Jesun amapa chu amun, kum sottah damlouva um ahi ahen, amapa jah a, “Nadam nom em?” ati.  
\v 7 Nakong chatmo pa chun, “Pu kadam joulou hila, twi akicholing teng twikul'a eikoi lhavah ding mi kaneipon, keima kacheji le kalhun masangin midang amasaji tai,” ati.  
\v 8 Chuin Jesun ajah a, “Kipat doh in, nalupna pheh kichoiyin, lam jottan!” ati.  
\v 9 Apettah chun mipa chu adamtan ahi, hichun aman alupna pheh chu akijel doh in lam ajottai, hiche thil kidang aso ni chu Cholngahni ahi.  
\v 10 Hijeh chun Judah vaipo hon hichu ajadauvin, akisudampa jah a “Cholngah nikhoa natoh phal ahipoi, nangman nalupna pheh nakichoiya lam najot chu dan ngai ahipoi,” atiuve.\x + \xo 5:10 \xt Nehemiah 13:19; Jeremiah 17:21\x*  
\v 11 Ahivangin amapan adonbut in ajah a, “Eisudampa ama tah in kajah a nalupna kichoiyin lam jottan eiti chula em,” ati.  
\v 12 Chuin ama hon, “Koi ham najah a chutia sei chu?” atiuve.  
\v 13 Ahinla mipa chun, asudampa chu koi ahi ahepoi, ajeh chu Jesu mipi lah a achelut mangtan ahi.  
\v 14 Ahivangin chom khat jouvin, Jesun amapa chu Hou-In'ah amun ajah a, “Tua hi akisudam nahitai; chonse kit tahih in, ajole akhohjo cheh na chunga chuget inte,” ati.  
\v 15 Chuin mipa chun Judah vaipo ho jah a ama sudam chu Jesu ahi ti agasei tan ahi.  
\v 16 Hijeh chun Judah vaipo hon Jesu ama tah in Cholngah nikho apalkeh jeh in, achunga bolsetna apan tauvin ahi.  
\v 17 Ahivangin Jesun adonbut in, “Kapan aphat jousen na atongin, keiman jong katong jinge,” ati.  
\v 18 Hiche jeh tah chun, Judah vaipo hon Jesu thana ding aha hol cheh tauvin ahi, ajeh chu aman Cholngah nikho apalkeh keo hilouvin, Pathen chu apa ahisah a chuleh Pathen toh kibanga aum jeh chu ahi.   
\s1 Pathen chapa thuneina  
\p
\v 19 Hijeh chun Jesun ahilchen in, ajah uva, “Thutah chu nangho ka seipeh nahiuve, Chapa chun ama cham cham in ima abolpoi. Pan abol amu ho chacha bou chu aman abolji ahi. Hijeh chun Pan abol jouse chu, Chapan jong abol ahi.  
\v 20 Ajeh chu Pan chapa chu angailun, anatoh athilbol jouse avetsah in ahi. Chule tahbeh in Pa chun hiche mipa kisuhdamna sanga chungnungjo avetsah ding ahi, hichu nang hon kidang nasah cheh dingu ahi.  
\v 21 Ajeh chu Pan mithi ho akaithouva ahinsah ji bang chun Chapan jong ahinsah nom ho chu hinna apeh ji ahi.  
\v 22 Chuleh Pan koima thu atanpoi, aman thutanna leh thuneina jouse abon'a Chapa apeh ahitai.  
\v 23 Hiti ahijeh chun, mijousen Pa ajabol banga Chapa chu ajabol cheh ding ahi; ajeh chu Chapa jabol lou chun ahinsol'a Pa chu ajabol lou ahi.”  
\v 24 “Keiman atahbeh chu nangho ka seipeh nahiuve, ka thusei ngaiya chuleh eisolpa Pathen tahsan'a chun tonsot hinna anei ahitai; amaho chu a itih a chonset themmo channa geita louva thina akon'a hinna galkai ahi tauve.”  
\v 25 “Chuleh keiman nangho tahbeh a ka seipeh nahiuve, phat chu ahung lhunge, tuhi ahi, mithi hon ka aw (Pathen Chapa aw) ajah ding'u, chuleh aja chengse hing ding ahiuve.  
\v 26 Ajeh chu Pa chun ama'a hinna anei ahin, chuleh aman hiche hinna pe thaneina chu Chapa apeh ahitai.  
\v 27 Chuleh aman mijouse chung'a thutanna leh thuneina chu chapa apeh ahitai, ajeh chu ama Mihem Chapa ahi.  
\v 28 Hijeh chun nangho lungdong hih un, phat chu ahung lhunge, lhankhuh a mithi ho jousen Pathen chapa aw ajah ding'u;  
\v 29 chuleh amaho thoukit diu ahi. Thilpha bol ho chu tonsot hinna a thoukit ding, chule thil phalou bol ho chu thupi tanna a themmo chang'a thoukit ding ahiuve.\x + \xo 5:29 \xt Daniel 12:2\x*  
\v 30 Chuleh keiman kacham in ima kabol theipoi, Pathen'in eisei peh banga thutanna kanei ahijeh in, ka thutan chu dihtah ahi, ajeh chu keima lunggot lam hilouva eisolpa ama lunggot lam'a kabol ahi.”  
\v 31 “Chule ka chungthu chu keima man ka hettohsah leh kathu hettohsah chu adih a pomthei hilou ding ahi.  
\v 32 Ahivangin keima chungthu chu midang khat in jong a hettohsah a ahileh tahbeh a ka seipeh nahiuve, amapan a hettohsah keima chungthu jouse chu adih ahi.  
\v 33 Chuleh nang hon John Baptist henga thu kholtoh dingin mi nasol'un, chuleh aman kachung chang thudihtah chu a hettohsah tai.\x + \xo 5:33 \xt Jn 1:19-27; 3:27-30\x*  
\v 34 Keiman mihem a kon hettohsah kangaipoi, ahivangin nangho huhhing'a naum na ding uva hiche hi kasei ahi.  
\v 35 John chu meivah koujing leh vahjing tobang ahin, chuleh ama thusei chu nang hon chomkhat dinga bou nalunglut piu ahi.  
\v 36 Ahivangin, keiman John sanga chungnungjo hettohsah kaneiye-hiche ka thuhil leh melchihna kidang kabol hi ahi. Chuleh Pan eisol lona photchenna dinga, hiche ho hi kabol dinga eipeh ahi.  
\v 37 Chuleh eihin sol'a Pa ama tah chun kachungthu a hettohsah ahitai, nang hon a imatih in ama aw najakha pouve, chuleh kimaito pin jong namukha pouve.\x + \xo 5:37 \xt Matt 3:17; Mk 1:11; Lk 3:22\x*  
\v 38 Chuleh nalung sung uva ama thusei achengpoi; ajeh chu aman nangho dinga ahinsol keima hi na tahsan pouve.”  
\v 39 “Nanghon Pathen Lekhabu thu nahol'un, ajeh chu hiche ho chun tonsot hinna napeh dan'un nagel uve, ahivangin Pathen Lekhabu'a thu chun, keima thudol'a hettohsah ahi bouve.  
\v 40 Ahivangin nang hon hiche hinna chu chan theina dingin keima henga nahung nom pouve.”  
\v 41 “Nangho phatsah peh chu keima dingin angaikhoh poi,  
\v 42 ijeh inem itileh, Pathen ngailutna chu nasung uvah achengpoi ti kahei.  
\v 43 Ajeh chu keima kapa min'a naheng uva kahung ahin, nang hon neisang pouve. Ahinlah midang ho chu amaho min'a naheng uva ahungleh kipahtah in nasang uve.  
\v 44 Chule nang hon na tahsan theilou chu datmo aumpoi, ajeh chu nang hon khat leh khat kijabolto na thanoppi uvin, Pathen khat seh ama ahung kon chu, jabol ding na khohsah pouve.”  
\v 45 “Hijeng jongleh Pa ang'a themmo achansah ding'u chu keima kahipoi; nang hon nakinep piu Mose chun themmona chan sah dingu ahi.  
\v 46 Chuleh nang hon Mose chu na tahsan tahtah u ahileh keima nei tahsan dingu ahi, ajeh chu aman keima thudol asut ahi bouve.  
\v 47 Ahivangin nang hon Mose chu na tahsan lou jeh un ka thusei ho hi nang hon iti na tahsan dingu ham?” ati.   
\c 6  
\s1 Jesun mi sangnga avahva  
\p
\v 1 Hiche jou hin, Jesu chun Galilee dillen, Tiberias dillen tia jong kihe agalkaiyin alangkhat achun achetan ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin mihonpi tamtah in, melchihna kidang abol ho leh anaho asuhdam amu jeh u chun achena chan'a anung ajui tauve.  
\v 3 Chuin Jesu chu mol chung khat a akal touvin, aseijui ho toh atoukhom uvin ahi.  
\v 4 Hichu Judah ho Kalchuh Kut nikho koncha ahitai.  
\v 5 Hichun mihonpi tamtah ama henglam jon'a ahung'u chu Jesun amun Philip jah a, “Mipi hijat neh ding changlhah hoiya ichoh dingu hitam?” ati.  
\v 6 Hiche hi Philip patepna a asei ahi bouve, aman abol ding ageltohsa ahitai.  
\v 7 Hichun Philip in adonbut in, “Eihon kum lhungin na tong jong leuhen mi hijat in themkhat khat a aneh khop u chohna ding kinga jou ponte,” ati.  
\v 8 Chuin Simon Peter sopipa, Andrew chun ajah uva.  
\v 9 “Hilaiya chapang khat in changlhah pheng nga leh nga ni aneiye, ahivangin mipi hijat lah a hicheng hi ipia pang kham ding ham,” ati.  
\v 10 Hichun Jesun ajah uva, “Miho jouse chu tousah un,” ati; chuin amaho chu abon'un hamhing chung'a chun atou tauve. (Numei chapang simlouvin mipilhing sangnga jen ahiuve).  
\v 11 Chuin Jesun changlhah chu alan, Pathen athangvah in miho hoppeh dingin apedohtai; chujouvin aman nga jong chutima chun abol in, chuleh mipi ho chun avaset cheh in ane tauve.  
\v 12 Hiti chun amitakip ava soh phat un, Jesun aseijui ho jah a, “Tun neh moh chengse loh khom'un, moh suhmang hih un,” ati.  
\v 13 Chuin ama hon changlhah pheng nga-a kon'a mipi nehmoh anong aval chengse aloh khom'un ahileh paipeh som le paipeh ni aloh dim'un ahi.  
\v 14 Chuin ama hon, Jesun hiche melchihna kidang abol chu amu phat un, atija behseh un, “Eihon themgao ina nga jingu chu ama hi ahi mong monge,” atiuve.  
\v 15 Chuin ama hon Jesu chu ada acham louva alengpau hisah ding agotauve, ti ahet jeh in, ama achangin thinglhang lam'a akilep mangtan ahi.   
\s1 Jesun twi chunga lam ajot  
\p
\v 16 Chuin nilhah ahiphat in aseijui te dillen pang lam'a acheuvin, Jesu angah tauve.  
\v 17 Ahivangin khothim geiya Jesu ahung kile lou phat in, amaho kongsunga alut un, Capernaum lam jon'in akitol tauvin ahi.  
\v 18 Chuin phulou helouvin hui hattah khat in amaho chu ahinno khum'in twi kinong chu asang jep asang jep in, akhohse lheh jengtai.  
\v 19 Hiti chun amaho mile li vel akitol lhungun, phulou helouvin Jesun amaho lam jon'a twi chunga lam ahinjot chu amu uve. Akicha lheh jeng'un,  
\v 20 ahivangin Jesun amaho akouvin, “Kicha hih un. Keima hichea kaum'e!” ati.  
\v 21 Chuphat in aseijui ten, Jesu chu kong sunga lutsah loi ding athanom'un hetmanlou kah chun ajotnau mun alhung tauve.   
\s1 Jesu hinna changlhah  
\p
\v 22 Ajingin dillen panga mihonpi umho chun, seijui hon kong khat umsun chu alah uva akitol'u chu amu uvin chuleh amaho lah a Jesu ajaopoi ti aheuvin ahi.  
\v 23 Chuleh Tiberias a kon'a hunglhung kong dang tamtah, Jesun changlhah phatthei aboh a mipin anehnau mun kom'a chu uma ahi.  
\v 24 Hijeh chun mihonpi chun, Jesu leh aseijui te chukom'a aum tapouve ti amu phat un amaho jong kong hoa chun alut un Jesu hol in Capernaum lang agalkai tauvin ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin ama hon dil gal lang khat a Jesu amu phat un, “Rabbi nangma itih a hilai mun nalhun ham?” atiuve.  
\v 26 Chuin Jesun amaho chu adonbut in, “Keiman nangho tahbeh a ka seipeh nahiuve, nang hon keima neihol'u hi neh ding changlhah kapeh jeh a bou ahin, melchihna kidang kabol ho nahet chen jeh uva ahipoi.  
\v 27 Hijeh chun, amang thahji neh ding holnan hibang lom'in kisugim hih un, hisang chun mihem chapan napeh ding'u tonsot hinna joh chu hol'in kisugim jouvin; ajeh chu Pa Pathen'in keima hiche dinga chu mohor einamdet ahitai,” ati.  
\v 28 Chuin ama hon adonbut un, “Keihon jong Pathen'a ding na katoh nom uve; ipi kabol dingu ham?” atiuve.  
\v 29 Jesun ajah uva, “Hiche bou hi Pathen'in nanghoa kon'a adei natoh chu ahi, ahinsolpa hi tahsan un,” ati.  
\v 30 Hichun ama hon adonbut un, “Nang katahsan theina ding'un ipi ham na bolthei melchihna kidang khat neimu sah un,” atiuve.  
\v 31 “Chule kapu kapateu chun gamthip ajotlaiyun manna aneuvin ahi, hichu Pathen Lekhabun asei Mose in amaho chu van'a konna changlhah neh ding apeuve,” kiti chu ahi.\x + \xo 6:31 \xt Potdohbu 16:4,15; Labu 78:24\x*  
\v 32 Chuin Jesun ajah uva, “Keiman nangho atahbeh ka seipeh nahiuve, Mose in van'a kon changlhah apekhapoi, kapan apeh ahi, chuleh tun nangho dingin van'a kon changlhah tahbeh chu apetai.  
\v 33 Pathen a kon'a changlhah tahbeh chu, van'a konna hung kumlha-a vannoiya hinna pea ama bou chu ahi.”  
\v 34 Chuin ama hon ajah a, “Pu chuche changlhah chu keiho aniseh in nei peuvin,” atiuve.  
\v 35 Jesun adonbut in, “Keima hinna changlhah kahi, koi hileh kahenga hung jouse gilkel kitlou ding, chuleh koi hileh keima eitahsan jouse a itih a dangchah kitlou ding ahi.”  
\v 36 Ahivangin nang hon keima neimu vang'un nei tahsan deh pouve.  
\v 37 Hijongleh, Paneipeh chengse ho chu kahenga hung ding ahiuve, chuleh keiman amaho chu kaledoh louhel ding ahi.  
\v 38 Ajeh chu keima eihin solpa Pathen lunglam bol dinga van'a kon'a hung kumlha kahin keima lunggot bol dinga hung kahipoi.  
\v 39 Chuleh Pathen lunglam chu hiche ahi, Aman keima eipeh chengse hi khatcha mansah louva, ninunung nileh amaho kakai thou ding ahi.  
\v 40 Ajeh chu hiche hi kapa lunglam ahi, Chapa mua chuleh tahsan jousen tonsot hinna anei ahitai; keiman amaho chu ninunung nileh kakai thou ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 41 Chuin Judah ho chu lunglhai lou tah in aphun gam tauve, ajeh chu Jesun, “Keima van'a kon'a hung kumlha hinna changlhah kahi,” ati.  
\v 42 Hichun amaho akihouvun, “Hiche pa hi Joseph chapa Jesu hilou ham? Apa leh anu kihe'a iti aman keima van'a kon'a hung kumlha kahi atithei ham?” atiuve.  
\v 43 Ahivangin Jesun adonbut in, “Kathusei ho jeh in phun hih un.  
\v 44 Ajeh chu keima eihinsol'a Pa chun kahenga aloilut ho tilou chu koima ama cham in, kahenga ahung theipoi, chuleh keiman amaho chu ninunung nileh kakai thou ding ahi.  
\v 45 Pathen Lekhabu'a 'Pathen'in amaho abon uva ahil ding ahi,' kiti bang chun, koi hileh Pa thu ngaiya chuleh ama a kon'a kihil ho bou chu kahenga hungji ahiuve.\x + \xo 6:45 \xt Isa 54:13\x*  
\v 46 (Chule koiman Pathen amu khapoi; Pathen'a kon hung kisol Keima bouvin Pathen chu kamu ahi.”)  
\v 47 Keiman nangho tahbeh a ka seipeh nahiuve, koi hileh ama tahsan chan chun tonsot hinna anei ahitai.  
\v 48 Ahi, Keima hinna changlhah kahi.  
\v 49 Napu napa teuvin gamthip a manna aneuvin, ahivangin amaho abon'un athi sohhel tauve.  
\v 50 Koi hileh van'a kon'a changlhah neho vang chu a itih a thi talou ding ahi.”  
\v 51 Keima van'a kon hung kumlha changlhah hing chu kahi, koi hileh hiche changlhah neho chu tonsot a hing ding ahi; chuleh vannoi hinna dinga kapeh ding changlhah chu katahsa hi ahi.”  
\v 52 Chuin miho chu khat leh khat Jesu thusei doh chun akinel'un, “Iti hiche pan atahsa chu eiho neh dinga apeh thei ding ham?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 53 Hichun Jesun adonbut in, “Keiman nangho tahbeh a ka seipeh nahiuve, nang hon Mihem Chapa sa naneh lou uva chuleh athisan nadonlou uleh, nasung uva tonsot hinna nanei lou dingu ahi.  
\v 54 Ahivangin koi hileh kasa ne'a, chuleh kathisan don'a vang chun tonsot hinna anei ahitai. Chuleh keiman ama chu ninunung nileh kakai thou ding ahi.  
\v 55 Ajeh chu neh ding tahbeh chu kasa ahin, chule don ding tahbeh chu kathisan ahi.  
\v 56 Hijeh chun koi hileh kasa ne'a chuleh kathisan don'a chu keima sunga ama aum'in chuleh ama sunga keima kaum'in ahi.  
\v 57 Chule eihinsol'a hingjing Pa jal'a keima hing kahi; hiche bang chun keima'a kon'a kivah chu keima jal'a hing ding ahi.  
\v 58 Ajeh chu keima van'a kon'a hung kumlha changlhah tahbeh chu kahi, hijeh chun koi hileh hiche changlhah ne-a chu, napu napa teuvin Manna ana neh uva athi sohhel'u bang hita louva, amaho chu tonsot a hingjing ding ahiuve.”  
\v 59 Thu hicheng hi aman Capernaum kho a kikhopna in'a athuhil pet a asei ahi.   
\s1 Asopi hon Jesu atahsan lou  
\p
\v 60 Chuin aseijui ten ajah a, “Hiche thu hi hetchen ahahsa val'e koiman sangthei ponte,” atiuve.  
\v 61 Hichun Jesun aseijui te alung himo thim'u chu ahen, ajah uva, “Hiche ka thusei hin nalungu asuh noh phah hitam?  
\v 62 Achutileh nang hon Mihem Chapa van'a lahtouva aum mukit leu chun, ipi nati tadiuvem?  
\v 63 Lhagao bouvin tonsot hinna apehji ahi, Mihem tahsa kihabol in ima abukim joupoi, chuleh keiman najah uva kasei doh thucheng ho hi, abon'a Lhagao leh hinna thu ahi.  
\v 64 Ahivangin nalah uva keima eitahsan lou naum uve,” ati. (Ajeh chu Jesun atil'a pat a koi ham ama tahsan lou chuleh koiham ama pedoh ding ti ahetsa ahitai.)  
\v 65 Chuin aman ajah uva, “Hiche jeh a chu Pan eipeh lou chu mi koima kahenga ahung theipoi, tia kasei ahi,” ati.  
\v 66 Hiche apat chun, aseijui ho tamtah ache mangun, ama adalha tauvin ahi.  
\v 67 Chuin Jesun som le ni ho jah a adongin, “Nanghon jong nei dalhah dingu ham?” ati.  
\v 68 Hichun Simon Peter in adonbut in, “Pakai koi henga kache ding'u ham? Tonsot hinna pe-a thunei nangbou nahi.\x + \xo 6:68 \xt Matt 16:16; Mk 8:29; Lk 9:20\x*  
\v 69 Keihon nangma Pathen theng khat seh nahi kaheuve, hichu katahsan uve,” ati.  
\v 70 Chuin Jesun ajah uva, “Keiman nangho som le ni kalhendoh nahiuvin, ahivangin nalah uva satan khat aum'e!” ati.  
\v 71 Hichu aman alhen doh som le ni ho lah a Simon Iscariot chapa Judas in khonunga ama apehdoh ding aseina ahi.   
\b  
\b  
\c 7  
\s1 Jesu leh asopi te  
\p
\v 1 Hiche jou chun, Jesun Galilee gamsung muntin achon'in avahlen ahi, ajeh chu Judah vaipo hon ama tha dinga agot jeh un, ama Judea gam'a chun aumnom tapon ahi.  
\v 2 Ahivangin hiche pet chu Judah te Lhambuh Kut kon cha ahijeh chun,\x + \xo 7:2 \xt Thempu Dan 23:34; Danbu Ni Na 16:13\x*  
\v 3 Asopi ten Jesu jah a, “Hilai mun dalhan lang Judea gam'a chen, chukom'a chu na seijui ten thil kidang nabol ho hi amuthei ding'u ahi.  
\v 4 Hitia nakisel leh iti namin kithang ding ham? Hitobang thil kidang ho hi nabol ding leh vannoi kimu sah in,” atiuve.  
\v 5 Ajeh chu asopi ho jengin jong ama chu atahsan lou ahi.  
\v 6 Hichun Jesun adonbut in, “Tuhi kei chena dinga phatpha ahipoi, ahivangin nangho chena dingin phat jouse ahitheiye.  
\v 7 Chuleh vannoiyin nangho nadou pouve, keima bou eidou'u ahi, ajeh chu ama hon setna aboljeh uva kaphoji ahi.  
\v 8 Chule nangho cheuvin, keima chethei ponge, ajeh chu keima phat alhing jeppoi,” ati.  
\v 9 Chule thil hicheng aseijou chun Jesu Galilee gam'a aumden in ahi.   
\s1 Lhambuh Kut laiya Jesu  
\p
\v 10 Ahivangin asopiho kut a achejou nung'un, mipi ho kimusah louvin, Jesu jong guhthim in achen ahi.  
\v 11 Kut lai chun Judah vaipo hon Jesu chu ahol'un, mipi lah a khat khat henga chun Jesu namu em? tin adong leuvin ahi.  
\v 12 Hichun mipi ho lah a, Jesu chung chang kinel baotamna asohdoh tan ahi, mi phabep chun, Jesu chu mipha ahi, atiuvin, ahivangin adang phabep chun Jesu chu imacha hilou mi lhem chavai bou ahi, atiuvin ahi.  
\v 13 Ahivangin Judah vaipo hon abol genthei diu ginna jal chun, Jesu thudol panpina mipi maiya ngamtah a seiphong ding koima aum pouvin ahi.  
\v 14 Chuin kut kibol kimlai tah chun, Jesu Hou-In'ah ache touvin chuleh thu ahilpan tan ahi.  
\v 15 Athusei ajah u chun Judah ho chu alungdong lheh un, “Hiche pa hin kijilna neilouhel 'a iti thil hijat hi ahet ham?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 16 Hijeh chun Jesun ajah uva, “Ka thuhil hi keima cham'a hung kon ahipon, eihin sol'a Pathen'a kon ahi.  
\v 17 Koi hileh Pathen lunglam hol'a bol ding go'a chun ka thuhil hi keima cham'a ham ahilouleh Pathen'a kon ham ti ahet ding ahi.  
\v 18 Ajeh chu ama cham'a thuhil chun, ama chang kichoi-atna adeiyun, ahivangin ahinsolpa jabolna leh choi-atna holpa vang chun thutah asei ahi, ama a chun jou aumpoi.  
\v 19 Mose in danthu napeh u ahin, ahivangin nangho khat in jong najui pouve, nang hon keima tha tahtah dinga neigot jingu ahi,” ati.  
\v 20 Chuin mipi chun adonbut un, “Koiham nang tha dinga nagong'ah? Nang hi thilhavop nahi bouve,” atiuve.  
\v 21 Jesun adonbut in, “Keiman Cholngah nikhoa thil kidang khat kabolin, nang hon nadatmo lheh uve.  
\v 22 Ahivangin nang hon jong nabol uve, Mose dan thupeh palkeh lou bangtah in Cholngah nikhon mi chep natan peh jiuve. (Tahbeh in, cheptan hi Mose dan thupeh um masanga napului teuvin ana phudohsa ahitai.)\x + \xo 7:22 \xt Thempu Dan 12:3; \xt Semtilbu 17:10\x*  
\v 23 Chuleh nang hon nachapa teu cheptan nikho chu Cholngahni atokhah jongleh Mose dan thupeh palkeh lou bangin hichu nabol jiuve, achutile ipi dinga keiman Cholngah nikho'a mi ka suhdam chu nang hon na lunghan piu ham?\x + \xo 7:23 \xt Jn 5:9\x*  
\v 24 Kun’un lang veuvin, chutileh dihtah a thu natan thei ding’u ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Jesu chu Messiah ham?  
\p
\v 25 Hichun Jerusalem miho chu amaho leh amaho akidongto uvin, “Vaipo hon tha dinga agot jing'u chu hiche pa hi hilou ham?  
\v 26 Amapa la hilaiya aum in, phongtah in mipi lah a thu aseiyin, chuleh vaipo hon jong ima alopouve. Achutileh ama hon jong hiche pa hi Messiah ahi ti apom ngap u ahi tadem?  
\v 27 Ahivangin amapa hi hichu iti hithei ding ham? Eihon ama ahung konna kihe sohkeiya, Messiah vang chu ahung tengleh koiman ahung konna ahetlou ding, hung kilah jeng ding ahi bouve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 28 Chuin Jesun Hou-In'a athuhil pet chun, ajah uva, “Adih e, nang hon keima neihe uve, chuleh kahung konna jong naheuve, ahivangin keima kacham'a hilaiya um kahipoi, keima eihinsolpa chu thudihtah ahi, chuleh nang hon ama chu nahe pouve.  
\v 29 Ahivangin keiman ama kahe chen'e, ajeh chu keima ama a hung kon kahi, chuleh aman keima naheng uva eihinsol ahi,” ati.  
\v 30 Chuin vaipo hon ama chu mat ding agouvin, ahivangin ama phat alhin loulai jeh in, koiman achunga khut alha pouve.  
\v 31 Hichun Hou-In'a um mi tamtah chun Jesu atahsan tauve, chule amaho akihouvun, “Messiah ahung teng, hiche pan abol kalval'a nasajo melchihna kidang abolnah ding ham?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 32 Chuin mihonpi chu, Jesu thudol akihou lhih melmul'u chu Pharisee hon ajahdoh phat un, thempu pipuiho toh kijaton, Jesu man dingin Hou-In ngah ho chu asol tauvin ahi.  
\v 33 Ahivangin Jesun ajah uva, “Keima nangho toh phat chomcha bou kaum khom ding ahi, chuleh keima eihinsolpa heng'a kakile kit ding ahi.  
\v 34 Nanghon keima neihol'un natin, neimulou dingu ahi, chuleh keima chena a chu nangho nahung theilou dingu ahi,” ati.  
\v 35 Chuin Judah vaipo ho chun, hiche Jesu thusei chu adatmo lheh un ahi, amaho akidong touvin, “Hiche pa hi hoilanga che ding kigo ham? Oleh, ama hi hiche gam dalha a mun danga um Judah ho henga che ding kigo ahidem? Ama hin Greek miho jeng jong agahil got hinte.  
\v 36 Chuleh ipi aseina mong ahidem? Nanghon neihol'un natin, neimulou dingu chuleh keima chena'a chu nangho nahung theilou dingu atihi,” akitiuvin ahi.  
\v 37 Chuin kut kichaini aniloupi pen nin, Jesu mihonpi lah a ading doh in, ajah uva, “Koi hileh adangchah a chu kahenga hunghen!\x + \xo 7:37 \xt Thempu Dan 23:36\x*  
\v 38 Koi hileh keima eitahsan'a chu kahenga hunghen chuleh hungdon hen! Ajeh chu Pathen Lekhabun aphondoh banga 'ama lungsunga kon'a chu twi hing luiya longdoh ding ahi,'” tin asamtai.\x + \xo 7:38 \xt Ezekiel 47:1; Zechariah 14:8\x*  
\v 39 (Aman “twi hing,” ati chu ama tahsan jouse chunga Lhagao aum ding aseina ahi. Ahivangin Jesu chu aloupina a alut loulai jeh in hiche Lhagao chu kipe loulai ahiuve.)  
\v 40 Chuin mihonpi chun, hiche asei chu ajauvin, alah uva phabep chun, “Hiche pa hi inga jingu themgao pa chu hitei jinte,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 41 Chuleh adang phabep chun, “Amapa hi Messiah ahi,” atiuvin ahi, ahivangin adang phabep chun, “Hiponte, iti Messiah chu Galilee gam'a hungsoh doh thei ding ham?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 42 Ajeh chu Pathen Lekhabu a kicheh tah a kiphongdohsa bangin, Messiah chu David chilhah hi ding, David khopi Bethlehem a kon hi ding ahi bouve, atiuvin ahi.\x + \xo 7:42 \xt 2 Samuel 7:12; Micah 5:2\x*  
\v 43 Hijeh chun, Jesu chung chang thua, mihonpi chu akikhen tel gam tauvin ahi.  
\v 44 Chuleh alah uva mi phabep chun, Jesu chu mat tei ding angaito uvin, ahivangin koiman achunga khut alhapouve.   
\s1 Judah vaipo hon Jesu atahsan lou  
\p
\v 45 Chuin Hou-In ngah sottol le ho chu Jesu manlouva ahung kile phat'un, thempu pipuiho leh Pharisee ho chun ajah uva, “Ibol'a ama nahin puilut lou uham?” tin adongun ahi.  
\v 46 Hou-In ngah sottol le hon adonbut'un, “Keihon hiche pa thusei tobang kaja khapouve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 47 Hichun Pharisee hon anuisat un, “Nangho jong lhep lhah a na um'u hitam?  
\v 48 Eiho lah a vaipo ho leh Pharisee ho khat beh injong amapa chu atahsan em?  
\v 49 Khohelou mihonpi in dan thupeh ima ahetlou jeh uva ama nung ajuiyu ahi bouve, chuleh achung uva Pathen sapset chuding ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 50 Hichun masanga Jesu toh gakimuto sa vaipo lah a khat amin Nicodemus chun, ajah uva;\x + \xo 7:50 \xt Jn 3:1,2\x*  
\v 51 “Mikhat chu ama thu kija masa louva, achunga themmo chansah jeng chu dan ngaina ham?” ati.  
\v 52 Chuin ama hon adonbut un, “Nang jong Galilee mi nahim? Pathen Lekhabua phet inlang sim'in Galilee gam'a kon'a themgao sohdoh khalouhel ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 53 Hichun akikhop nau aki khen'un mijousen a in cheh akijot tauvin ahi.   
\c 8  
\s1 Ajonpet tah a kiman numei  
\p
\v 1 Jesu chu Olive lhang lam'a akile kittai.  
\v 2 Ahivangin ajing jingkah matah in ama Hou-In'ah ahungkit in ahi. Chuin hetman louvin, mihonpi khat aheng'a ahung kikhom'un ama atouvin, amaho chu thu ahiltan ahi.  
\v 3 Hitia athuhil laitah chun, Danthu themho leh Pharisee hon, ajonpet tah a kiman numei khat ahin kaiyun, mipi lailunga chun adinsah un ahi.  
\v 4 Hichun ama hon Jesu jah a, “Houhil, hiche numei hi ajon pettah a kiman ahi.  
\v 5 Hijeh chun Mose dan thupeh dungjuijin, amanu hi songa selih ding ahi, nangman ipi nagel em?” atiuve.\x + \xo 8:5 \xt Thempu Dan 20:10; Danbu Ni Na 22:22-24\x*  
\v 6 Hichu ama hehsetna thei ding ikhat beh aseidoh khat leh tia thangkam peh ahiuve; ahivangin Jesu akun'in ima seilouvin akhut jungin tol chu ajih in ahi.  
\v 7 Hichun ama hon Jesu chun adonbut tei dinga ano jeh un Jesu ading doh in ajah uva, “Aphai, nalah uva chonset bolkha louhel pen penin amanu chu songin sep masa hen!” ati.  
\v 8 Chuin ama akun'in tol chu ajihkit in ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin ama hon hichu ajah phat un, atehpen'a pat aneopen geiyin amaho khat khat in achemang gam tauvin, mihonpi lailunga chun Jesu changseh leh numeinu bou adalha tauvin ahi.  
\v 10 Hichun Jesu adingdoh in amanu jah a, “Nahin kaiho hoilam gei hitauvem? Koiman themmo nachan lou hitam?” ati.  
\v 11 Hichun amanun, “Pakai, koiman themmo eichan tapoi,” ati. Hichun Jesun amanu jah a, “Keiman jong themmo kachan tapoi, chetan ahin tukal chonse kit tahih in,” ati.   
\s1 Jesu vannoi vah  
\p
\v 12 Chuin Jesun avelin miho jah a, “Keima vannoi vah kahi. Kanung najui uleh nangho muthim'a vahle lou nahi tauve, ajeh chu nang hon hinna vah chu naneiyu ahitai,” ati.\x + \xo 8:12 \xt Matt 5:14; Jn 9:5\x*  
\v 13 Hichun Pharisee hon adonbut un, “Na chungthu nangma tah in na hettohsah chu hettohsah dih ahipoi,” atiuve.\x + \xo 8:13 \xt Jn 5:31\x*  
\v 14 Hichun Jesun ajah uva, “Ka chungthu keima tah in ka hettohsah hi, hettohsah dihtah ahi. Ajeh chu keiman kahung konna leh kajotna ding kakihet in, ahivangin hichu nang hon nahe pouve.  
\v 15 Chule nang hon tahsa mihem hina dol'in ka chungthu natan'un, keiman vang koima chungthu chuti chun katan jipoi.  
\v 16 Ijem tia thutanna kabol tah jong le, kathu tan jouse abon'a dihtah ahi; ajeh chu keima kachang kahipon, eihinsol'a Kapa toh kahi lhon'e.  
\v 17 Ajeh chu nangho danthu dungjuijin minin kitoh tah a a hettohsah leh hichu hettohsah dihtah a kipom ahi.\x + \xo 8:17 \xt Danbu Ni Na 19:15\x*  
\v 18 Hijeh chun, keima tah hettohsah khat kahin, chuleh eihinsol'a kapa chu hettohsah adang khat chu ahi.”  
\v 19 Hichun ama hon adong'un, “Napa hoiya um ham?” atiuve, Jesun adonbut in, “Nanghon keima neihet lou jeh un, Kapa koi ahi jong nahe pouve. Keima neihe leu chun, Kapa jong nahet diu ahi,” ati.  
\v 20 Hicheng jouse chu, Jesun Hou-In sunga sumkholna kiti mun'a athuhil pet a asei ahi. Ahivangin anikho alhin jep loulai jeh in, koiman ama chu amanpoi.  
\v 21 Chujouvin Jesun avel in ajah uva, “Keima kache mang ding ahi. Nangho kache na a nahung thei pouve, ajeh chu na chonset nau chu nathipi ding'u ahi,” ati.  
\v 22 Hichun miho chu akidong touvin, “Hiche pa hi ama leh ama kithat go khat ham? Chuleh kache na a nangho nahung thei pouve ati hi ipi aseina ahidem?” atiuve.  
\v 23 Chuin Jesun avel in ajah uva, “Nangho noiya kon nahiuvin; keima chunga kon kahi. Chuleh nangho hiche vannoiya um nahiuvin, keima kahipoi.  
\v 24 Hiche jeh a chu najah uva kasei ahi, nang hon keima koi kahi ka hettohsah hi na tahsan lou uleh, na chonset nau chu nathipi tei ding'u ahi,” ati.  
\v 25 Hichun ama hon adong'un, Nang koi nahim? atiuve, Jesun adonbut in, “Keima ama chu kahi tia kasei jing tah chula em, ati.  
\v 26 Keiman nangho chunga demna ding leh sei ding adim'in kaneiye, ahivangin seipong e; ajeh chu keima eisolpa chu thudihtah ahin, ama a kon'a kajah ho bou kasei ahi.”  
\v 27 Ahivangin Jesun hiche asei chu, Pa thudol aseina ahi ti ama hon ahedoh thei deh pouve.  
\v 28 Hiche jeh chun, Jesun ajah uva, “Nanghon Mihem Chapa chu thingpel a nadop sang teng'u leh, ama chu keima tah kahi nahet dingu ahi. Ajeh chu keiman kacham'a imacha kabolpon Pa chun eihil ho bou kasei ahi.  
\v 29 Chuleh keima eisolpa chun eiumpi jinge, aman kachangin eidalha poi, ajeh chu keiman phat jousen ama lunglhaina bou kabol jin ahi,” ati.  
\v 30 Chuin mi tamtah in thu hicheng asei chu ajah phat un, ama chu atahsan tauve.   
\s1 Thutah chun nalha ong diu ahi  
\p
\v 31 Hichun Jesun ama tahsan ho henga chun, “Nangho ka thuhil'a hi kitah tah a na um jing'u leh nangho kaseijui tahbeh nahiuve.  
\v 32 Chuleh nang hon thutah chu heuvin natin, chuteng thutah chun na chamlhat sah dingu ahi,” ati.  
\v 33 Hichun ama hon, ajah a, “Keiho vang Abraham son leh pah kahiuve, keiho imatih in koima soh in kaum khapouve; nangho na chamlhat sah ding'u nati chu ipi naseina ham?” atiuvin ahi.\x + \xo 8:33 \xt Matt 3:9; Lk 3:8\x*  
\v 34 Jesun adonbut in, “Keiman atahbeh chu ka seipeh nahiuve, koi hileh chonset bol jinga chu chonset soh ahi.  
\v 35 Chuleh soh chu insungmi tahtah ahiden theipoi, ahin chapa vang chu a itih a insungmi dihtah ahi jinge.  
\v 36 Hijeh chun, Chapa chun nangho nalha-ong uva ahileh nangho achamlhat tahbeh nahiu ahitai.  
\v 37 Adih e, nangho Abraham son leh pah nahiu kahenai; ahivangin nang hon keima tha ding neigo jing uve, ajeh chu nalung sung uva ka thuhil hi alutpoi.  
\v 38 Chuleh keiman kapa kom'a kamu chengse nangho ka seipeh nahiuve, ahivangin nang hon napau thumop bou najui uve.”   
\s1 Napau chu satan ahi  
\p
\v 39 Ama hon adonbut un, “Kapau chu Abraham ahi,” atiuve, hichun Jesun ajah uva, “Ahipoi,” nangho Abraham chate hileu chun, ama thilbol nung najui dingu ahi.  
\v 40 Ahinlah keiman Pathen'a kon'a kajah thutah cheng nangho ka seipeh jeh un, nang hon keima tha ding neigo jing uve, Abraham chun imatih chanin chutobang thil abolpoi.  
\v 41 “Nanghon napau dihtah adang khat umchan najui'u ahi bouve,” ati. Hichun ama hon adonbut un, “Keiho jaocha kahi pouve, Pathen ama tah chu kapau dihtah ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 42 Hichun Jesun ajah uva, “Pathen chu napau ahileh, nang hon keima nei ngailut dingu ahi. Ajeh chu keima Pathen'a kon hung kipan kahi. Keima kacham'a hung kahipoi, aman eihin sol ahi bouve.  
\v 43 Chuleh nang hon ibol'a ka thusei nahet thei lou uham? hiche hi nang hon ka thusei na ngailou jeh u ahi.  
\v 44 Nangho napau Satan chate nahi jeh un, ama thilbol aphalou ho bol ding na nomui, ama chu atil'a pat a tolthat ahin, ama a thutah aumlou jeh chun, phat jousen aman thutah ahot in ahi; aman jou asei chu achonna 'a behden ahitai, ajeh chu ama mijou ahin, jou kondohna pa ahi.  
\v 45 Hijeh a chu keiman nangho thutah ka seipeh u jongleh, nang hon keima nei tahsan theilou u ahi!  
\v 46 Chuleh nangho koipen in hettohsah kichehtah a michonse kahina nei ngoh thei uvem? Achutileh naheng uva keiman thutah kasei ahi, ibol'a nei tahsan lou uham?  
\v 47 Hijeh chun koi hileh Pathen'a hiho chun kipah tah in Pathen thu angaiyun ahi; ahivangin nangho Pathen'a nahilou jeh un athu na ngai pouve,” ati.   
\s1 Abraham masanga ana umsa  
\p
\v 48 Chuin ama hon ajah a, “Nangma Samaria mi nahin, thilhavop nahi tia kana seijingu hita lou ham?” atiuve.  
\v 49 Jesun adonbut in, “Kahipoi, keima thilhavop kahipoi. Ajeh chu keiman kapa kajabol ahin nang hon keima nei jabol pouve.  
\v 50 Ahivangin, keiman keima chang kichoi-at kaholpoi, Pathen'in keima eichoi sang ding bou ahi; ajeh chu ama thutan dihtah ahi.  
\v 51 Chule keiman nangho atahbeh chu ka seipeh nahiuve, koi hileh ka thuhil ngaiya bol'a chu a itih a thilou ding ahi!” ati.  
\v 52 Chuin ama hon ajah a, “Thilhavop nahi kahe tauve, Abraham leh themgao ho athigam tauvin, ahivangin nangman ka thuhil nit a chu a itih a thilou ding ahi, nati.  
\v 53 Chule kapau Abraham sang'a chungnungjo nahim? Ama athitan, themgao ho jong athi tauvin, ahileh nangman koi kahi tia naki gel ham?” atiuve.  
\v 54 Hichun Jesun adonbut in, “Keima kichang choi-atna hol kahileh hichu keima ima hilou kahitai; ahinlah nang hon 'ka Pathen'u' natiu kapa ama chun keima ei choi-at ding ahi bouvin,  
\v 55 ahivangin nang hon ama chu nahe pouve. Kenvang ama chu kahei. Chuleh keiman ama chu kahepoi tileng keima tah hi nangho banga mijou kahi khah ding ahi! Ahivangin keiman ama kahet jeh chun ama thu kangaiyin ahi.  
\v 56 Napau Abraham chun keima nikho mu ding ana galdot ahi. Aman hichu anamun chuleh akipah lheh jengin ahi,” ati.  
\v 57 Chuin Judah ho chun ajah a, “Nangma kum somnga bon lhinglou laiya, iti nangin Abraham kamutai nati ham?” atiuve.  
\v 58 Jesun adonbut in, “Keiman nangho atahbeh ka seipeh nahiuve, Abraham masanga keima ana umsa jing kahitai,” ati.  
\v 59 Chuche phat chun, Judah hon ama sena dingin song akilah tauvin ahi, ahivangin alah uva kon'in Jesu chu akiseldoh in, Hou-In'a kon chun achemang tai.   
\c 9  
\s1 Apen a mitchoa peng khat aboldam  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Jesu chu avahlen ahileh, apen'a mitcho'a peng mikhat amun ahi.  
\v 2 Hichun aseijui ten ajah a, “Houhil, hiche pa hi ipi jeh a apen'a mitcho'a peng ham? Ama chonse ham? Oleh anu leh apa chonse a ham?” atiuve.  
\v 3 Jesun adonbut in, “Hiche hi ama chonset jeh jong ahipon anu leh apa chonset jeh jong ahipoi.” “Hiche hi Pathen thahatna ama chunga akiphkonna dinga ahi bouve.  
\v 4 Hijeh chun eihon kinloi tah a eisol pauvin einganse nau hi itoh dingu ahitai.  
\v 5 Ahivangin keima hiche vannoiya kaum laisea hi vannoi vah kahi,” ati.\x + \xo 9:5 \xt Matt 5:14; Jn 8:12\x*  
\v 6 Chuin aman tol'ah achil aset in, achil a chun bonlhoh asemin chuleh hiche bonlhoh chu mitchopa mit a aloiyin ahi.  
\v 7 Hichun aman ajah a, “Chen Siloam twikul'a nangma tah in gaki phetlhah in,” (Siloam chu “sol” tina ahi) ati. Hijeh chun mipa chu achen aga kiphetlhah tai, chuleh kho amun ahung kile tan ahi.  
\v 8 Chuin aheng akom achenkhompi ho chuleh masanga amapa khutdoji musa ho chu akidong touvin, “Toumun'a khutdoji pa chu hiche pa hi hilou ham?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 9 Mi phabep chun “Amapa chu ahi” atiuvin, chuleh adang phabep chun, “Amapa chu ahipoi akilopi joh ahi bouve,” atiuvin ahi; hichun amapa chun, “Henge ama chu kahinai,” ati jeng tan ahi.  
\v 10 Chuin ama hon adong'un, “koiham kho namu sah? ipi iti dan ham?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 11 Hichun amapan ajah uva, “Jesu atipau chun bonlhoh asemin, hichu kamit a eiloi peh in chuin kajah a ‘chen Siloam twikul'a nangma tah in gaki phetlhah tan eiti,’ hijeh chun keima kachen kaga phetlhah leh kho kahin mu ahitai,” ati.  
\v 12 Chuin ama hon adongun, “Amapa chu tua hoiya um tam?” atiuvin ahi, aman adonbut in, “Kahepoi,” ati.   
\s1 Pharisee hon mitchopa khomu dol akhol u  
\p
\v 13 Chuin ama hon masanga mitcho pa chu Pharisee ho henga ahinpui tauvin ahi.  
\v 14 Ajeh chu Jesun bonlhoh asem'a amapa asuhdam nikho chu Cholngahni ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin Pharisee hon amapa chu amit khomu dol abonchan adongun ahi, hijeh chun aman ajah uva, “Aman bonlhoh chu kamit a aloiyin, chuin keiman kaga phetlhah leh kho kamu jeng ahitai,” ati.  
\v 16 Chuin Pharisee ho phabep chun, “Hiche mipa Jesu hi Pathen a kon ahipoi, ajeh chu aman Cholngah nikho apalkeh e atiuvin ahi.” Ahivangin adang phabep chun, “Iti michonse khat in hitobang melchihna kidang ho hi abolthei ding ham?” atiuvin, amaho lah a chun kibung khenna lentah aumdoh tan ahi.  
\v 17 Chuin Pharisee hon, mitcho kho mupa chu adong kit un, “Namit kho namu sahpa chu nangman koi ahi natim?” atiuvin, aman adonbut in, “Themgao khat hiteiyinte,” ati.  
\v 18 Hiche jeng jong chun, Judah vaipo hon hiche mipa chu, mitcho anahia tua kho amu ahitai, tichu atahsan pouve, hijeh chun ama hon anu leh apa akimu piuvin ahi.  
\v 19 Chuleh ama hon anu leh apa chu adong'un, “Hiche pa hi apen'a mitchoa peng'a hinam? Ahileh tua iti kho amuthei ham?” atiuve.  
\v 20 Hichun anu leh apan adonbut in, “Amahi apen'a mitchoa peng kachapa lhon ahi, kahe lhon e,” ati.  
\v 21 “Ahivangin aman iti kho amu ham, koiyin amit adamsah ham, kahe lhonpoi; ama dong'un, ama tah achungthu kiseitheiya upa ahitai,” atilhon e.  
\v 22 Hichu anu leh apan Judah vaipo ho kichatna jeh a achuti seilhon ahi, ajeh chu ama hon, “Koi hileh Jesu chu Messiah ahi tia sei aum leh kikhopna in'a kon'a nomang ding tia ana phondoh sau ahitai.”  
\v 23 Hiche jeh a chu amanin ajah uva, “Ama kidoh un ama tah chu athu kisei theija len ahitai,” atilhon ahi.  
\v 24 Chuin ama hon anivei nan mitcho khomupa chu akouvun, ajah a, “Hiche thua hi Pathen bou loupi sah in, ajeh chu Jesu kitipa chu michonse ahi, keihon kaheuve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 25 Hichun aman adonbut in, “Ama michonse ahi ahilou kahepoi, ahivangin kahet chu hiche ahi, ‘keima mitcho kana hin tunvang kho kamutai,’” ati.  
\v 26 Chuin ama hon adongkit tei teiyun, “Ama chun ipi abol'a iti namit chu asuhdam ham?” atiuve.  
\v 27 Aman ajah uva, “Veuvin khatvei kaseisa ahitai, nang hon nangai pouve, ibol'a avel'a najah nom kit uham? Nangho jong ama seijui nahi nom'u ham?” ati.  
\v 28 Chuin ama hon mipa chu agaosap un, ajah a, “Nangbou ama seijui nahin, keiho vang Mose seijui kahiuve.  
\v 29 Pathen'in Mose heng'a thu asei chu kaheuve, ahinlah hiche pa hi hoiya hungkon koi ahi kahe pouve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 30 Chuin amapan adonbut in, “Hichu datmo umtah ahi, aman kamit kho musahta a ahivanga nang hon ama hung konna nahetlou u chu;  
\v 31 Pathen'in michonse ho thu angaipoi, ahivangin ama guttah a houva alunglam bol ho thu bou angaiye, ti iheuve.  
\v 32 Chuleh vannoi leiset umtil apat koiham khat in, apen'a mitchoa peng kho amusah lam akija khapoi.  
\v 33 Hiche pa hi Pathen'a kon ahilouleh aman hitobang hi abolthei louhel ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 34 Hichun ama hon adonbut un, “Nang napum'a chonse sa a peng'a nangin keiho neihil got uham?” atiuvin, kikhopna in'a kon chun anodoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 35 Jesun thilsoh umchan chu ajan, chuin mipa chu amun, ajah a, “Nangman Mihem Chapa chu na tahsan em?” ati.  
\v 36 Amapan adonbut in, “Pu, ama chu koi ham? Keiman katahsan ding nati chu,” ati.  
\v 37 Chuin Jesun adonbut in ajah a, “Nangman ama chu namutai, chuleh nahenga thuseiya hi ama chu ahi!” ati.  
\v 38 Hiche pettah chun mipa chun, ajah a, “Henge Pakai katahsan e,” atin, Jesu chu chibai abohtai.  
\v 39 Chuin Jesun amapa jah a, “Keima mitcho hon kho amu uva chuleh khomu a kigel ahivanga la mitcho, hon akigeldoh theina ding uva thutan dinga vannoiya hung kahi,” ati.  
\v 40 Hichun avel'a um Pharisee hon ajah a, “Keiho hi mitcho nei hisah uham?” atiuve.  
\v 41 Jesun adonbut in, “Mitcho hileu chun chonsetna naneilou dingu ahin, tunvang nang hon kho kamui nati jeh un nachung uva chonset um ahitai,” ati.   
\c 10  
\s1 Jesu kelngoi chingpha  
\p
\v 1 “Keiman atahbeh ka seipeh nahiuve, koi hileh kelngoi hongkot a lut louva bang'a kal'a hunglut chu gucha michom ahi!  
\v 2 Ahivangin kelngoi hongkot a hunglut amavang chu kelngoi chingpa ahi.  
\v 3 Ama chu kot ngahpan kot ahonpeh jin, chuleh kelngoi hon ama aw aheuvin, aheng'a ahung jiuve, chule aman akelngoite chu amin cheh in akouvin, apuidoh jin ahi.  
\v 4 Chule aman akelngoi ho ahoidoh soh tengleh, amaho chu alamkaiyin, chuleh akelngoi hon anung ajui jiuve, ajeh chu ama hon amapa aw chu aheuve.  
\v 5 Chuleh kelngoi hon hetphahlou midang nungjui louhel ding ahiuve, ama a kon'a jammang ding ahiuve ajeh chu ama hon michom dang aw ahepouve.”  
\v 6 Jesun hiche thulem asei jaho chun, aman ipi aseina ahi ahepouvin,  
\v 7 hijeh chun Jesun ajah uva, asei chenin, “Keiman nangho atahbeh ka seipeh nahiuve, keima hi kelngoi hongkot chu kahi.  
\v 8 Ka masanga hung ho jouse abon uva gucha leh michom ahiuve. Ahinlah amaho thu chu kelngoi hon angaipeh pouve.  
\v 9 Henge, keima kelngoi hongkot chu kahi. Koi hileh keiya hunglut a chu huhhing'a um ding ahi. Amaho chu nom tah a lut le pot le dingu chuleh hamhing hoitah akimu dingu ahi.  
\v 10 Guchapa hunglona chu agu mang ding leh asumang ding bou ahi, keima vang ama hon ninglhinna leh lunglhaina hinkho aneina ding uva hunga kahi.”  
\v 11 “Keima kelngoi chingpha kahi, kelngoi chingpha chun akelngoite dingin ahinna apejin ahi.  
\v 12 Ahin thalah kelngoi chingpa vang chun, ngei hung amu teng ama ajamjin chuleh akelngoite adalha jitai; ajeh chu ama kelngoi chingtah ahipon, kelngoite jong ama a ahipoi, chutengleh ngei chun kelngoite chu adelkhum in aman in chuleh asucheh jitan ahi.  
\v 13 Ijeh inem itileh ama thalah kelngoi ching, sum mun'a ding bouva natong ahijeh chun, aman kelngoite ngailutna aneipoi.”  
\v 14 “Keima kelngoi chingpha kahi, keiman ka kelngoite kahen, chuleh ama hon keima eiheuve.\x + \xo 10:14 \xt Matt 11:27; Lk 10:22\x*  
\v 15 Kapan keima eihet tobang bangin keiman Pa chu kahei; hijeh chun, keiman ka kelngoite dingin ka hinna kapei.  
\v 16 Chuleh keiman hiche hong sunga umlou kelngoi dang jong kaneiye, chule keiman amaho jong chu kaga puilut ding chuleh ama hon ka-aw ahet dingu chuteng kelngoi ho chu honkhat hiuva achingpa jong khat seh hi ding ahi.”  
\v 17 “Pan keima eingailui, ajeh chu keiman ka hinna chu avel'a kilelah kit dinga kakatdoh tah jeh chun;  
\v 18 Khattouvin, keiya kon'a ka hinna chu eilahpeh thei ahipoi, keiman kacham'a kakatdoh ahi bouve, ajeh chu keiman katdohna le avel'a kile lah kit theina chu kanei ahi. Hichu kapan keima eithupeh ahi,” ati.  
\v 19 Aman thu hicheng asei jeh chun, Judah ho chu abung bungin akikhen kit tauve.  
\v 20 Alah uva phabep chun, “Hiche pa hi thilhavop ahin alunggel kisuhlou ahi bouve, chule ibol'a ama thusei kingai ding ham?” atiuve.  
\v 21 Chule adang phabep chun, “Athusei hi thilhavop um dan ahipoi, thilhan mitcho kho amusah ngaiyem?” atiuve.   
\s1 Juda Hon Jesu Asandau  
\p
\v 22 Hichu phalbilai ahin Hou-In katdohna kut abollaiyu ahin, Jesu Jerusalem'a aumpet ahi.  
\v 23 Ama Hou-In'a aum in, Solomon hongcha kiti laiya chun ama avahlen ahi.  
\v 24 Hichun Judah hon ama chu aumkimvel un, “Itihchan keiho lung hesoh a nei umsah ding'u ham? Nangma Messiah chu nahileh nei seipeh un,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 25 Jesun adonbut in, “Keiman nangho ka seipehsa ahitai, ahivangin nang hon nei tahsan pouve. Kapa min'a ka thilbol cheng hi Keima thudol hettohsah ahitai.  
\v 26 Ahivangin nangho ka kelngoite nahilou jeh un, keima nei tahsan pouve.  
\v 27 Keima kelngoi hon ka aw angaiyun, keiman amaho kahen, chuleh ama hon kanung eijui uve.  
\v 28 Keiman amaho chu tonsot hinna kapen, chuleh amaho chu itih a jong mangthah louding ahiuve. Chuleh koiman keiya kon'a amaho chu eilahpeh louding ahi.  
\v 29 Ajeh chu kapan amaho chu keima eipeh ahitai, chuleh kapa chu ima jouse'a thaneipen leh hatchungnung ahi. Koiman amaho chu kapa khut a kon'a alahpeh louding ahi.  
\v 30 Chuleh Pa leh keima chu khat seh kahi lhon e,” ati.  
\v 31 Chuin Judah hon ama selihna ding song akilo tauvin ahi.  
\v 32 Jesun ajah uva, “Kapa thusah bangtah a keiman thilpha tamtah kabol ahitai. Hoiche pentah jeh a chu nang hon keima song'a neise dingu ham?” ati.  
\v 33 Ama hon adonbut un, ajah a, “Keihon nang napha toh jeh a songa kase dingu nahipoi, Pathen na taitom jeh ahi bouve. Nangma mihem hiya Pathen naki hisah jeh ahi,” atiuve.\x + \xo 10:33 \xt Thempu Dan 24:16\x*  
\v 34 Jesun adonbut in, “Hiche hi nangho Pathen Lekhabua kisun hilou ham? Pathen'in mihem ho jah a anaseisa, 'nangho hi pathen ho nahiuve kiti chu kasei ahi!'.\x + \xo 10:34 \xt Labu 82:6\x*  
\v 35 Chuleh nang hon naheuve, Pathen Lekhabua kisun chu khel thei ahipoi. Hiche jeh chun, Pathen thu lhunna miho bon 'pathen ho' tia akikou thei leh;  
\v 36 ibol'a ken, 'keima Pathen chapa kahi' tia kasei leh nang hon Pathen taitom nahi neitiu ham? Pan hiche dinga chu keima atumbeh a eikhen doh a eisuhtheng'a vannoiya eihinsol ahi.  
\v 37 Eisol'a kapa natoh ho kabol louleh nei tahsan dauvin.  
\v 38 Ahin, ama kin katoh ahivang leh, keima nei tahsan theilou jongleh, melchihna kidang kabol ho hi hettohsah nan neiyun lang, tahsan un. Chutileh nang hon Pa keiya aum'a chuleh keima Pa a kaum chu hetauvin nate,” ati.  
\v 39 Chuin avel'in ama hon Jesu chu matding ago kit un, ahi. Ahivangin ama hiche mun'a kon chun apotdoh in amaho chu adalhatai.  
\v 40 Chuin ama Jordan lui gallam'a amasa a John in baptize ana bolna lam'a chun achen aga umtai.\x + \xo 10:40 \xt Jn 1:28\x*  
\v 41 Chua chun, mi tamtah in anung ajuiyun, amaho chu akihouvun, “John in melchihna kidang ho ana bolpon, ahivangin Jesu thudol aseiho abonchan atah in alhung sohkeiye,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 42 Chuin chukom'a um mi tamtah ho chun Jesu atahsan tauve.   
\c 11  
\s1 Lazarus thi  
\p
\v 1 Pasal khat amin Lazarus kitipa chu Bethany a cheng ahin, dammona nei, chule asopi teni Mary leh Martha toh cheng khom ahi.\x + \xo 11:1 \xt Lk 10:38,39\x*  
\v 2 Hiche numeinu Mary hi ahi, Pakai kengbul'a thao nua asama theh ngima chu;\x + \xo 11:2 \xt Jn 12:3\x*  
\v 3 Chule amanin a ucha lhonin Pakai Jesu heng'a thu athot lhon'in hitin asei lhon e, “Pakai na ngailut naloipa hi adammo lheh tai,” ati lhonin ahi.  
\v 4 Hichu Pakai Jesun ajah chun hitin aseiyin, “Lazarus dammona hi thina a kichai ding ahipoi. Ahipoi, Pathen loupina dinga kibol'a ahi bouvin hiche a konna chu Pathen Chapan loupina amu ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 5 Pakai Jesun, Mary, Martha leh asopipa Lazarus alungset lheh jeng vang chun;  
\v 6 Hikom'a aumna mun'a chun Pakai Jesu chu nini tobang aumbe nalaiyin ahi.  
\v 7 Achainan, Aman aseijui ho kom'a, “Judea gam'a kilekit tau hite,” ati.  
\v 8 Ahin aseijui ten lung opkaina aneiyun, “Rabbi, ni ijat ham khat masanga chu Judea gam'a mihon songa selih ding nagot u chula em,” atiuve.  
\v 9 Jesun adonbut in, “Nikhat sunga hi nidan som le ni niseh a um ahi. Sun a hi mijousen lam ajotthei cheh ding ahi. Ama hon kho amu theinau chu ahileh vannoi vah anei jeh u ahi.  
\v 10 Ahin, jan tengleh kipal lhuhna thei jong aum'e ajeh chu vah aum tapon ahi,” ati.  
\v 11 Hichun aman aseiyin, “Iloipau Lazarus a imu lhatai, amavang Keima kache ding kaga thodoh ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 12 Hichun seijui ten adonbut uvin, “Pakai, Lazarus chu a imut leh damvah ding tina ahitai,” atiuve.  
\v 13 Ahin seijui ho geldan'a chu kicholdo dinga a imut aseiyin angaitouvin, ahin Pakaiyin asei chu Lazarus thi ahitai atina ahi.  
\v 14 Hichun Pakaiyin aseichet peh in, “Lazarus chu athitai.  
\v 15 Chuleh keima kakipah lheh e, ajeh chu nang hon na tahsan theina dingu ahi. Hungun, ama gaveu hite,” ati.  
\v 16 Thomas aminlhem Apengkop kisahpa chun aseijui chan khompi ho jah a, “Eiho jong cheu hitin, chu a Pakai toh gathi khom'u hite,” ati.   
\s1 Jesu thokitna le hinna ahi  
\p
\v 17 Jesu Bethany kho ahung lhun chun Lazarus chu lhan khuh a avui nau nili ahitai ti aseipeh uve.  
\v 18 Bethany chu Jerusalem kom ahin, mile themkhat bouva gamla ahi;  
\v 19 Chuleh Judah le midang tamtah achekhom'un, Mary leh Martha amani lungmon sah dinga hung'ah anaum'un ahi.  
\v 20 Hiti chun Martha in Pakai ahungtai tithu ajah phat in amanu chu achen Pakai chu aga kimupin Mary vang chu inmun'ah aum dentai.  
\v 21 Hichun Martha in Jesu kom'a aseitai, “Pakai, nangma hilai mun'a hi ana um hile chun kasopipa hi thilou ding ahi” ati.  
\v 22 Ahin tun jong Pathen'in nathum chan napeh ding kahenai ati.  
\v 23 Jesun amanu jah a, “Nasopi pa thou kit ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 24 Marthan adonbut in, “Henge kanom'e, Ni nunung nia thokit nia atho doh kit ding chu kahe nai,” ati.  
\v 25 Hichun Jesun amanu jah a hitin aseiye, “Keima hi thokitna le hinna chu kahi. Koi hijongleh keima eitahsan chan chu thi tajongleh, thoudoh kit ding ahi.  
\v 26 Koi hijongleh keima a hinga chule keima eitahsan a chu thi louhel ding ahi. Martha, hiche hi na tahsan em?” ati.  
\v 27 Martha'n adonbut in, “Henge, Pakai, nangma hi Messiah, Pathen Chapa nahi chu ka tahsan jing'e, Pathen a kon vannoiya hunga chu nahi,” ati.   
\s1 Jesu akap e  
\p
\v 28 Hiche chu asei jouvin achemang in asopinu Mary guhthimin akouvin, “Houhil chu hikom'a aumin, nakouve,” ati.  
\v 29 Chuin Mary in hichu ajah jah in gangtah in akipat doh in ahenga achetai.  
\v 30 Pakai Jesu chu khopam'a Martha toh akimutona lhon a chu um nalai ahin;  
\v 31 Hichun mipi ho Mary lhamon dinga um hon ama akipat doh a kino thethua adalhah chu amu u chun Lazarus lhankhuh langa gakap dingin agel'un, hichun ama hon Mary nung chu ajuiyun ahi.  
\v 32 Hiti chun Mary chu Jesu umna alhun phat in ama chu amun akengphang bul'ah abohkhup jengin ajah a, “Pakai nangma hikom'a um hile chun kasopipa thilou dinga,” ati.  
\v 33 Hichun Jesun amanu aka amun ahin lhonpi mipi ho jong chu akau amun alungsunga lunghem tah le pohnatna neitah in aum uvin ahi.  
\v 34 Hichun Jesun amaho chu adongin, “Hoiya nakoiyu hitam?” ati. Mipi hon adonbut un, “Pakai hungven,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 35 Hichun Jesu akaptai.  
\v 36 Hikom mun vel'a ding ho chun aseiyun, “Veuvin iti angailut hitam,” atiuve.  
\v 37 Ahin koitobang loichun hitin aseiyun, “Hiche pa hin mitcho ho kho amusah hilou ham, chule Lazarus jong chu athida sah thei chula em,” atiuvin ahi.   
\s1 Lazarus ahindoh sahkit  
\p
\v 38 Hichun Jesu chun lhan khuh ahin phah chun lunghem tah in aum in; chuleh alhan chu kohom khat ahin, akot chu song khat a kising ahi.  
\v 39 Jesun amaho jah a aseiyin, “Song chu tangdoh un,” ati. Chule athipa sopinu Martha chun ajah a, “Pakai, tun a uitai, ijeh inem itile nili ahitai,” ati.  
\v 40 Hijeh chun Jesun adonbut in, “Natahsan'u leh Pathen loupina namu dingu ahi kati hilou ham?” ati.  
\v 41 Hichun ama hon songpi chu atangdoh tauvin, hichun Jesun vanlam aven “Pa, nangman kataona na ngai jeh in namin ka thangvah e;  
\v 42 chuleh nangman kataona na ngai jinge, ti keiman kahenai, ajeh chu kakimvel a mipi ding ho hin nangma sol kahi hi ahin tahsan theina ding uva kati ahi bouve,” ati.  
\v 43 Hichun Jesun hasap tah in asam in, “Vo Lazarus, hung thoudoh in,” ati.  
\v 44 Hichun Lazarus chu akhut akeng lhanpon a kitom pumin amai ultheh pon a kitom pumin lhan khuh a kon'in ahungdoh tan ahi. Hichun Jesun ajah uva, “Lhamun lang lam jotsah un,” ati.   
\s1 Jesu thana ding agon u  
\p
\v 45 Hichun mipi tamtah Mary toh um jouse chun athilbol chu amu uvin hichun Jesu chu atahsan tauve.  
\v 46 Ahin mipi lah a mi kimkhat acheuvin Pharisee ho jah a Jesu thilbol chengse chu agasei tauve.  
\v 47 Hijeh chun thempu pipuiho leh Pharisee ho houvaipo loi akikhom'un, “Eihon ipi ibol'u ham? Hiche pa khun la melchihna tamtah abol jing jengin ahi.  
\v 48 Eihon ama hi tua banga iche jomsah jingu le mijousen ama ahin tahsan cheh cheh dingu, hiche teng chule Rome solkal in eiho inam'u ahin i-Hou-In'u ahin eisuhchim peh dingu ahitai” atiuve.  
\v 49 Hiche laiphat tah a thempua ana pang chu Caiaphas ahin aman hitin aseiye, “Nanghon na thuseiyu hi ipi kiseina ham nahe pouve ati.  
\v 50 Chujongleh vannoi pumpi aboncha amanthah louna dinga miho dinga mikhat athi nangho dinga phajo ahi, tijong nagel pouve,” ati.  
\v 51 Chuleh hiche ho hi Caiaphas in ama chama aseidoh ahipon, thempu pipui hina a gaova aphondoh a, Pakai Jesu hin vannoi nam jouse khel'a ahinkho apehdoh ding thu asei masah ahi bouve.  
\v 52 Chuleh Israel chate kisuh khom ding seh hilouvin, namtin jouse le Pathen chate jouse akikhop khoma pumkhat ahidohna dinga jong ahi.  
\v 53 Hiti ahijeh chun, hichea pat chun Juda ten Jesu thana ding lung angaito uvin akihousom tauve.  
\v 54 Hijeh chun Jesu Judah ho lah a lhangphongin avahle tapoi; chua kon chun Jerusalem adalhan, gamthip lama Ephraim khoa aseijuiho toh chua chun aum jing tauve.  
\v 55 Chuleh Judah te Kalchuh Kut ahung naitan, hichun kut masanga kisutheng dingin gamsunga Judah te jousen, Jerusalem ahin jon cheh tauvin ahi.  
\v 56 ama hon Jesu ahol'un, Hou-In vel'a adin uchun, khat le khat akihouvun, “Ipi na ngaito uvem? Jesu chu kut a hi hung louding ham?” akitiuve.  
\v 57 Hichun thempu pipuiho leh Pharisee hon, lhangphong tah in aphongun, koi hijongleh Jesu umna hea chun amat theina ding uva avetsah ding uvin mipi ho thu apeuvin ahi.   
\c 12  
\s1 Bethany khoa Jesu thao anu  
\p
\v 1 Kalchuh Kut kipatna ding nigup masang'in, athi a konna athodoh Lazarus umna Bethany a chun Jesu ahungin,  
\v 2 Hiti chun ama dingin jan an asemun, chuleh Marthan ajenlen Lazarus vang chu ankonga ama toh touho lah a chun apangin ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin Mary in halpi bei Bego thao namtui man tamtah chu ahin choiyin Jesu kengphanga anun asamin atheh ngimin ahileh agimnam chun insung chu alosoh jengin ahi.\x + \xo 12:3 \xt Lk 7:37,38\x*  
\v 4 Chuin seijuiho lah a khat Simon chapa Judas Iscariot, amatsah a pang dingpa chun,  
\v 5 “Hiche thao namtui hi manlutah ahi. Man tamtah a joh a mivaicha gentheiho peh ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 6 Aman hiche ati chu vaicha genthei khohsah a asei ahipoi, ama chu gucha ahin, chule sumdip avop ahin, asunga kikoi chu akilahji ahi.  
\v 7 Hichun Jesun adonbut in, “Amanu chu achangin dalha uvin. Kakivui nia dinga kigontup theina a abol ahi.  
\v 8 Nanghon genthei chaga aphat seh a nanei jing dingu ahi, ahin keima vang aphat seh a nangho lah a umjou louding kahi,” ati.\x + \xo 12:8 \xt Danbu Ni Na 15:11\x*   
\s1 Lazarus tha dia agon u  
\p
\v 9 Chuin mipi hon Jesu chukom'a ahunge ti ajah phat un, Judah ho mi tamtah ama chung chang jeng hilouvin, athilah a konna athodoh Lazarus jong chu venomin ahenga ahung tauve.  
\v 10 Hichun thempu pipui hon Lazarus jeng jong thadoh dingin agongun ahi.  
\v 11 Ajeh chu amapa jeh tah a jong chu miho lah a tamtah pin amaho anuse uva Jesu atahsan u ahitan ahi.   
\s1 Jesu loupi tah a Jerusalem alut  
\p
\v 12 Hiche ni ajingin kut a dinga hung mipi atama tamin, Jesu Jerusalem'a dingin ahunge, ti ajah phat un,  
\v 13 Lusu na akidop un aga lamto uvin, “Hosana, Pakai min a hunga Israel te Lengpa chu anunnome,” tin asam asamun ahi.\x + \xo 12:13 \xt Labu 118:25,26\x*  
\v 14 Chuin Jesun sangan chalgol khat amun, achunga atouvin ahi;  
\v 15 “Vo Zion chanu, kicha hih in; Ven, na lengpa sangan nou chunga atouvin ahunge,” tia kisun bang chun.\x + \xo 12:15 \xt Zechariah 9:9\x*  
\v 16 Hicheng thu chu Jesu seijui ten amasan ana hepouvin ahi, ahin Jesu choiat a aumdoh phat chun, hiche thu chu ama thudol'a kisunsa ahin, ama hon hitia chu abol'u ahi tichu ageldoh tauve.  
\v 17 Hichun aman Lazarus akouva athi lah a konna athodoh pettah a aumpi mipi chengse chu athu hettohsah a pang ahiuve.  
\v 18 Hiche melchihna abol ajah jeh tah uva chu mipi chun alamtou ahi.  
\v 19 Hichun Pharisee ho khat le khat akihou lim un, “Veuvin eihon imacha ibol thei dingu aumpoi; ajeh chu mijousen ama nung ajui cheh tauve,” atiuvin ahi.   
\s1 Greek mihon Jesu amunom u  
\p
\v 20 Hiche Kalchuh Kut a chu Pathen hou dinga Greek mi phabep khat chetou ahiuvin;  
\v 21 Hichun amaho Galilee gam'a Bethsaida khoa mi Philip henga ahungun ajah a, “Pu, Jesu chu kamu nomui,” ahung tiuve.  
\v 22 Hichun Philip ahungin Andrew jah a ahung seiyin, chuin Andrew ahungin Philip toh Jesu jah a asei lhone.  
\v 23 Jesun adonbut in, “Mihem Chapa choiat a aum ding phat ahunglhung e.  
\v 24 Thutah kaseipeh nahiuve, chang malkhat chu tol'a tulut in aumjie. Hichu athilou le achangin aumden ji bouve; athi vang le tamtah agajin ahi.  
\v 25 Koi hijongleh hiche vannoi leiset chunga ahinkho itcha ho chu mangthah ding ahi; ahin koi hijongleh hiche vannoi leiset chunga ahinkho pedoh ho chun tonsot hinkemlou anei dingu ahi.\x + \xo 12:25 \xt Matt 10:39; 16:25; Mk 8:35; Lk 9:24; 17:33\x*  
\v 26 Koi hijongleh kalhacha a panga chun kanung eijuihen, keima umna a chu kalhacha jong um ding ahi; mi koi hile kalhacha a panga chu Pa chun ajabol ding ahi.”   
\s1 Mihem chapa kidomsang tei ding ahi  
\p
\v 27 “Tun kalung adongtai; ipi kati ding ham? 'Pa, hiche nidan a kon hin nei huhdoh in.' Ahivangin hiche dinga hi hung kahi.  
\v 28 “Pa, namin choian'in” ati. Hiche chun van'a kon'in Aw ahung gingin, “ka choian tai, chule choian kit nalai ding kahi,” ati.  
\v 29 Hiche chun akimvel a ding mipi chun hichu ajauvin, “Van aginge,” atiuvin; adangsen, “Vantil in ajah a thu asei ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 30 Jesun amaho jah a, “Hiche awgin najah u chu nangma ho phatchomna ding ahi bouve, keima a ding ahipoi.  
\v 31 Hiche vannoi leiset chunga thutanna phat ahunglhung tai, Satan vannoiya vaihompa nodohna phat jong hunglhung ding ahitai.”  
\v 32 Chule keima leiset a konna ka thodoh tengleh keiman mijouse kahenga dinga kahung pui ding nahiuve.”  
\v 33 Hichu aman athi ding dan tahlangna a hitia chu asei ahi.  
\v 34 Mihonpi chun adonbut in, “Keihon la Messiah chu tonsot a hingjing ding ahi, ti Pathen Lekhabua kon'in kaheuvin; Ipi jeh a Mihem Chapa thi ding ahi nati thei ham? Hiche Mihem Chapa chu amonga koi ham?” atiuve;\x + \xo 12:34 \xt Labu 110:4; Isa 9:7; Ezekiel 37:25; Daniel 7:14\x*  
\v 35 Jesun adonbut in, “Kavah hi nalah uva chomkhat bou um nalai ding ahi; muthim in naphah louna dingun vah umpet hin vahle uvin; muthima vahlea chun achena ding ahepoi.  
\v 36 Vah nanei pet chau hin vah chate nahi theina dingun vah chu tahsanun,” ati. Thu hicheng chu aseiyin, apotdoh in amahoa kon chun akisel tai.”   
\s1 Juda ten Jesu atahsan lou u  
\p
\v 37 Isaiah themgao thusei: “Pakai ka thuseiyu kon atahsan em? Chule Pakai ban thahat koi henga kilang am?”  
\v 38 Tia asei chu guilhun theina ding chun, a angsung uva melchihna kidang tamtah abolin, ahivangin atahsan pouve.\x + \xo 12:38 \xt Isa 53:1\x*  
\v 39 Hiche thua hin Isaiah themgao chun avel in aseikit in:  
\v 40 “Aman amit u asuchon, alungu asutah tai; achuti loule amit un mu uvin tin, chule alungun heuvin tin, chule hung kihei kit un tin keiman boldam get inge,” ati; hiche jeh a hi ama hon atahsan theilou u ahi.\x + \xo 12:40 \xt Isa 6:10\x*  
\v 41 Isaiah chun aloupi chu amu jeh a hicheng chu aseiya; amaho thudol chu asei ahi.  
\v 42 Achuti vang'in vaipo ho jeng jong tamtah in atahsan tauve; ahinla Pharisee ho jeh chun kikhopna a kon'in eiki kaidoh khante, tin aseidoh aum pouve.  
\v 43 Ajeh chu ama hon Pathen choiat sangin mihem choiat adei jouvin ahi.   
\s1 Jesu thuseiya thu kitan  
\p
\v 44 Hichun Jesun aw sangtah in asam in, “Koi hijongleh keima eitahsan chun keima hilouva eisolpa joh atahsan ahi bouve;  
\v 45 Chule keima eimua chun eisolpa amu ahi.  
\v 46 Koi hijongleh keima eitahsan a chu muthim a aum louna dinga keima vah hina a vannoiya hung kahi.  
\v 47 Mikhat touvin kathu jahen nit hih jong le athu katanpoi; ijeh inem itile keima vannoi thutan'a hung kahipoi, vannoi huhhing ding joh a hung kahi bouve.  
\v 48 Koi hijongleh keima eipampaiya ka thuhil jong joplou chu, thupi kitan nile thutah kaseidoh hin achungthu atan ding ahi.  
\v 49 Ijeh inem itile keiman kacham'a kasei ahipoi, eisol'a Pa chun kasei ding le kapao ding dan hi thu eipeh ahi bouve.  
\v 50 Ama thupeh chu tonsot hinna ahi, ti kahei; hiche jeh a chu ka thusei hi Pan eihil bang banga kasei ahi,” ati.   
\c 13  
\s1 Jesun seijui ho kengphang asilpeh  
\p
\v 1 Kalchuh Kut masangin Jesun hiche vannoiya konna apa henga ache ding phat ahunglhung tai, ti ahen, vannoiya um ama a ho chu angailun akhonni geiyin angailu lhumkeiye.  
\v 2 Chuin jan anneh lai sungin diabol chun Simon chapa Judas Iscariot lungsunga ama matsahna ding lungthim khumsa akoi ahitan;  
\v 3 Jesun, Pan thil jouse ama khut a apeh chule ama Pathen a konna hungdoh ahia, Pathen henga chea ahi chu ahen;  
\v 4 Ajan anneh ankonga kon'in akipat doh in chuin aponsil akong'ah akigah in ahi.  
\v 5 Chuin aman kisilna kong'ah twi alheiyin, aseijui ho keng asil'in, akong gahna pon chun atheh peh in ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin ama Simon Peter kom'a ahungin ahile aman ajah a, “Pakai nangman kakeng nei silpeh ding ham?” atin ahile,  
\v 7 Jesun adonbut in, “Kabol hi nangman tun nahepoi, ahin ni phabep jouleh henan nate,” ati.  
\v 8 Chuin Peter in ajah a, “Nangman itih hijongleh kakeng nasil louhel ding ahi,” ati. Jesun adonbut in ajah a, “Keiman nangma kasillou le keiya nangman chan nanei lou ahi,” ati.  
\v 9 Simon Peter in ajah a, “Pakai kakeng keojeng hilouvin kakhut le kalu jonge,” ati.  
\v 10 Jesun adonbut in, “Apumpia kisil khat chu akeng tailou adang sil ding angai khohpoi; apumpin angim sohnai. Chule nangho na ngim nauve, ahivangin na bonchau nahi pouve,” ati.  
\v 11 Ijeh inem itile ama matsah a pang dingpa chu aman ahetsa ahin, hiche jeh a chu aman, “Nabon chauvin na ngim pouve,” ati ahi.  
\v 12 Aman akengu asil jouvin apon akilah in atou kit in amaho jah a chun, “Ipi bol'a kahi chu nahet nah uvem?\x + \xo 13:12 \xt Lk 22:27\x*  
\v 13 Nanghon keima 'Houhil' le 'Pakai' neitiuve. hiche natiu chu adih e, ijeh inem itile keima hichu kahi.  
\v 14 Hijeh chun keima 'Pakai' le 'Houhil,' jengin bon nangho keng kasil le nang hon jong khat in khat keng naki silpehto dingu thu ahi.  
\v 15 Ajeh chu keiman nangho kabol banga chu nang hon jong nabolna ding uva vetsahna a kabol ahi.  
\v 16 Tahbeh a kaseipeh nahiuve, soh ho apupau sangin achungnungjo poi. Asol'a sangin solchah jong achungnungjo poi.\x + \xo 13:16 \xt Matt 10:24; Lk 6:40; Jn 15:20\x*  
\v 17 Hiti ho hi nahetdoh uva nabol'u le nangho anunnom nahiuve.”  
\v 18 “Nangho na boncha uva thudol'a kasei ahipoi; keiman ka lhendoh ho chengse chu kahenai; ahivangin, 'Ka changlhah nepan kachunga akengto alamtai,' ti Pathen Lekhabua thu guilhun theina dinga ahi.\x + \xo 13:18 \xt Labu 41:9\x*  
\v 19 Tua kal'a ahung guilhun tengleh keima hi Messiah chu kahi. Nahetna ding uva ahung guilhun masanga ka seipeh nahiuve.  
\v 20 Tahbeh a koi hijongleh kasolna a nom chan chun keima eisan ahi; chule keima eisang chan chun Pa asan ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 13:20 \xt Matt 10:40; Mk 9:37; Lk 9:48; 10:16\x*   
\s1 Min ajoh ding Jesun asei masah  
\p
\v 21 Hichun Jesu alungdong lheh jengin aseitai, “Atahbeh a nangho lah a mikhat in nei johdoh dingu ahi!” tin ahin seidoh e.  
\v 22 Hichun seijui ho chu khat le khat akiveto uvin, koi asei ahi agelmo uve.  
\v 23 Hiche a chu aseijui ho lah a khat Jesun angailut chu a-ang a ki-ngai ahin;  
\v 24 Simon Peter in akhasuh in, “Koi nasei ham nei seipeh un,” ati.  
\v 25 Hichun ama akingai bang chun akingaiyin, “Pakai hiche chu koi ham?” tin adongin ahile;  
\v 26 Jesun adonbut in, “Hiche changlhah hal hi kade a kapeh ding pen tah chu ama chu ahi,” ati. Chuin aman changlhah hal chu adekot jouvin alan Simon chapa Iscariot Judas chu apetai.  
\v 27 Chuche changlhah hal akisan joutah chun Satan asunga alut tan, chuphat chun Jesun ajah a, “Nabol ding chu bol loiyin,” ati.  
\v 28 Ahivangin aman ipi dol'a achuti sei ahidem, ankonga touho khatchan jong ahedoh pouve.  
\v 29 Ijeh inem itile kimkhat in Judas khut a sumbom aum jeh a chu kut a dinga manchah ding choa, ahilou le vaichaho ikhat pe dinga Jesun aseiyin angaito uve.  
\v 30 Chuin aman changlhah hal chu akisanin hiche pettah chun apotdoh pai jengtai. Hichu jan ahi.   
\s1 Thupeh thah  
\p
\v 31 Ama apotdoh chun Jesun, “Mihem Chapa choiat in aumtai, ama ah Pathen jong choian'in aumtai;  
\v 32 Chule Pathen'in jong Chapa jeh a choi-atna amu jeh a, aman chapa chu achoiat pai jeng ding ahi.”  
\v 33 Chapang neocha ho nangho toh chomcha khat bou um ding kahi, nang hon neihol dingu, ahivanga Juda ho jah a kasei “Keima chena a chu nangho nahung theilou dingu,” kati ahi.\x + \xo 13:33 \xt Jn 7:34\x*  
\v 34 “Keiman nangho thupeh thah kapeh nahiuve, nangho khat le khat kingailuto cheh un; keiman nangho kangailut bangu hin, nangho jong khat le khat kingailu uvin.\x + \xo 13:34 \xt Jn 15:12,17; 1 Jn 3:23; 2 Jn 1:5\x*  
\v 35 Nangho khat le khat naki ngailutto cheh uva ahile hichun keima seijui nahiu vannoiya na tahlang'u ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Peter in aseilep ding Jesun asei masah  
\p
\v 36 Simon Peter in adongin, “Pakai nangma hoilam'a nache ding ham?” atile Jesun adonbut in, “Tun nangma kache na a kanung nunga hung thei pon nate, phat chomkhat jou teng vang leh kanung nunga nahung ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 37 Peter in ajah a “Pakai ibol'a tua nanung nunga kahung theilou ding ham? Nangma jal'in ka hinna jong penge,” ati.  
\v 38 Jesun adonbut in, “Kei jal’a thi ding? Tahbeh a kaseipeh nahi, Peter___jing jingkah ahchal khon masanga, neihenasa a thumvei nei seilep ding ahi,” ati.   
\c 14  
\s1 Jesu, Pathen heng jotna lampi  
\p
\v 1 “Nalung'u khamsah hih un. Pathen tahsan'un, chule keima jong nei tahsan'un.  
\v 2 Kapa in'ah chenna ding indan ninglhingset in aum'e; umlou hile najah uva kasei tah hih ding ham? Ajeh chu keima nangho dinga mun sema che ding kahi.  
\v 3 Thil jouse gontup ahi tengleh, keima hung ingting, kaumna a chu naum jing theina diuva kahung pui ding nahiuve.  
\v 4 Chule nang hon kachena ding mun alampi nahe nauve,” ati.  
\v 5 Thomas in adonbut in, “Pakai keihon na chena ding bon kihelou a alampi iti kahet dingu ham?” ati.  
\v 6 Jesun amapa chu adonbut in, “Keima hi lampi le thutah chule hinna chu kahi; keima henga pat tailouvin koima Pa kom ahung theipoi.  
\v 7 Chule nang hon keima nei heleu chun Kapa jong chu nahet dingu ahitai; tu apat a vang nang hon amapa chu naheuvin chule namu tauve!” ati.  
\v 8 Hichun Philip in adonbut in, “Pakai, Pa chu neimu sah un, hichu keiho dinga phaset ahi,” ati.  
\v 9 Jesun adonbut in, “Philip, keima hitih chan nangho toh kaum khom a jong chu neihet loulai ham? Chule keima eimua chun Ka-Pa amu ahitai; achutile Pa chu neimu sah-un iti nati ham?  
\v 10 Chule keima Pa a kaum a chule Pa jong keiya um ahi, hiche hi na tahsan lou ham? Chule keiman nangho jah a thu kasei chengse hi keima cham'a kasei ahipoi; Pa chu keiya uma na atoh ahi bouve.  
\v 11 Keima Pa a kauma chule Pa jong keiya aum'e ti chu nei tahsan jengun; ahilou jong le nakitong chengse jeh tah hin tahsanun.”  
\v 12 “Atahbeh a, keima eitahsan'a chun ka thilbol chengse hi aman jong abol ding ahi; asanga lenjo jo abol ding ahi, chule keima Pa henga kinung lekit ding kahitai.  
\v 13 Chule Pa chu Chapan achoiat a, chule nang hon thil jouse ipi hijongleh Keima min'a nathum chanu chu kabol peh ding nahiuve.  
\v 14 Chule Keima min'a nathum dingu chu ipi hijongleh ka bolpeh ding nahiuve!” ati.   
\s1 Jesun Lhagao Theng hungkum ding atep  
\p
\v 15 “Keima nei ngailut uleh ka thupeh ho hi nanit dingu ahi.  
\v 16 Keima Pa henga taoving ting chuleh aman nangho naumpi jing dingu Lhamonsah Lhagao napeh dingu ahi.  
\v 17 Ama chu Lhagao Theng, thudih lampia napui uva ahi; vannoiyin ama chu asang theipoi; ijeh inem itile ama chu mu jong amu pouvin, he jong ahe pouve; nang hon vang naheuve, ajeh chu ama nangho sunga chenga ahi, um jong hung um ding ahi.  
\v 18 Chule keiman nangho avetup ding beiyin na dalha pouvinge; keima naheng uva hung kit ding kahi.  
\v 19 Vannoi mihon phat chomkhat jou le eimu tahlou dingu ahi, ahinla nang hon vang neimu dingu ahinai; Ajeh chu keima kahing jinge, chule nangho jong nahin dingu ahi.  
\v 20 Keima hinna a ka thodoh kit teng, nang hon nahet chen diu ahi; keima Pa a kaum'a chule nangho keima a naum diu chule keima nangho a kaum ding ahi.  
\v 21 Koi hijongleh ka thupeh ho neiya chule nit chu eingailua ahi; chule keima eingailua chu ka Pan angailut ding; chule keiman ama chu ka ngailut a ahenga kaki phon ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 22 Judas (Iscariot hilou, seijui achom khatpa) chun ajah a, “Pakai, ibol'a nangma keiho henga naki phon'a vannoi mi henga naki phon louding ham?” ati.  
\v 23 Jesun adonbut in ajah a, “Eingailu jouse chun kathu anit ding, chule ka Pan amaho chu angailut ding, chule aheng uva kahunga amaho chu kachenpi ding ahi,  
\v 24 Chule koi hijongleh keima eingailu lou chun kathu jong anitpoi; chule nathu jah uhi keiya ahipoi, eisola Pa a chu ahi bouve.  
\v 25 Keiman nangho kaumpi pet a thu hicheng hi ka seipeh nahiuve.  
\v 26 Ahinla Pan keima khel'a naki thopi dingu Lhagao Theng ahinsol teng, Ama chun thil jouse nahetsah dingu chule thil jouse ka seidoh ho jouse avel'a nagel dohsah kit dingu ahi.”  
\v 27 “Lungmon ka dalhah peh nahiuve; kalungmon kapeh nahiuve; kapeh hi vannoi mi peh bang ahipoi; nalungu donsah hih-un, kicha jong kicha hih-un.  
\v 28 Naheng uva thu kana seiho geldoh jing uvin ajeh chu keima kache mang ding ahin, ahin naheng uva kahung kit ding ahi; chule keima nei ngailut mong ule kei sanga laljo Pa kom'a kache ding hi nang hon nei kipapi joh dingu ahi.  
\v 29 Hiche ho hi naheng uva ka seipeh masat u ahi, Ajeh chu thil ho hi ahungso phat tengleh nang hon na tahsan theina dingu ahi.”  
\v 30 “Nangho toh kihou limna ding phat kanei lhomtai, ajeh chu vannoi leiset chunga vaihompa ahung nai tai, aman ka chungah tha aneipoi.  
\v 31 Amavang Pan keiya konna angaichat chu kabol ding ahi, chutile vannoi in Pa ngailutna hi ahin hetthei dingu ahi, hung uvin eiho che jengu hite.”   
\c 15  
\s1 Jesu, lengpi gui tahbeh  
\p
\v 1 “Keima lengpi gui kahi, chule kapa hi alhoungim hon neipa ahi.  
\v 2 Chuleh keiya um abah aga louho chu aman apaidohji; chuleh aga chengse chu ahaga chehna dingin amalngim jin ahi.  
\v 3 Kathusei vanga chu nangho angimsa nahi tauve.  
\v 4 Chuleh nangho keiya um jingun, keijong nanghoa um inge, abah lengpi guiya aumlou le achanga aga theilou banga chu nangho jong keiya naum lou ule naga theilou dingu ahi.”  
\v 5 “Henge, keima hi lengpi gui chu kahi, nangho abah nahiuve. Keiya umho chule keiman jong kaumpi jouse chun ga tamtah ahin sosah dingu ahi. Ajeh chu keima louvin nang hon imacha nabol thei pouve.  
\v 6 Mi keiya umlou chu panna bei abah bangin paidoh in aumjin, chuleh agop jin chuleh achom khomun meikong sungah aseplut jiuvin ahile akavam jitai.  
\v 7 Ahin nangho keima a naum jing uva, chuleh keima thucheng ho nangho a aum le, nang hon na ngaichat chan'u nathum thei u ahi; chuleh naki bolpeh dingu ahi.  
\v 8 Nanghon theiga tamtah napunsah teng'ule keima seijui dihtah nahiuve, hiche jeh a chu Pa choiat na um ding ahi.”  
\v 9 “Pan keima eingailut bang banga keiman jong nangho ka ngailut nahiuve, hijeh chun kangailutna a hin um jingun.  
\v 10 Nanghon keima thupeh napom teng ule keima ngailutna a um nahi tauve; chule keiman jong hitobanga Pa thupeh kanit jing jeh a, ama ngailutna a um jing kahi.  
\v 11 Kakipana nangho a aum jingna ding le nakipa nau achamkim na dinga thu hicheng hi najah uva kana sei ahi!  
\v 12 Hiche hi keima thupeh ahi, Keiman nangho kangailut bangin, nangho jong khat le khat kingailuto cheh in um'un.\x + \xo 15:12 \xt Jn 13:34; 15:17; 1 Jn 3:23; 2 Jn 1:5\x*  
\v 13 Min ajol agol dinga ahinna apeh sanga ngailut chungnungjo koiman aneipoi.  
\v 14 Ka thupeh ngai ho chu kaloi ahi.  
\v 15 Keiman nangho soh kati louding nahi tauve, ajeh chu soh in apupa thilbol ahepoi; tua nangho hi kaloi ngaitah nahiuve, ajeh chu Pan keima eihetsah jouse nangho ka seipeh nahi tauve.  
\v 16 Nanghon keima neilhen'u ahipoi, Keima joh in nangho kalhen doh a nacheuva haga nagauva chuleh nagau aumna dinga kapansah nahiuve. Ipi hijongleh nagot chanu kamin a Pa henga nathumu chu aman napeh theina dingun.  
\v 17 Hiche hi keima thupeh ahi, nangho khat le khat kingailuto cheh un,” ati.   
\s1 Vannoi mite vetdana  
\p
\v 18 “Vannoiyin nahin vetda tengule geldoh un keima eivetda masat u ahi.  
\v 19 Nangho vannoiya hileu chun vannoiyin ama a chu angailut ding ahin; tunla nangho vannoiya nahilou u, vannoiya konna keiman ka lhendoh nahiuvin, hiche jeh a chu vannoiyin nahot u ahi.  
\v 20 Thu kanahil uchu nahet nahlai uvem? 'Soh apakai sangin achungnungjo poi.' Ama hon kei eibolse uva chu nangho nabolset dingu ahi; kathu nit leu nangho thu jong anit dingu ahi.\x + \xo 15:20 \xt Matt 10:24; Lk 6:40; Jn 13:16\x*  
\v 21 ama hon keima jeh a hiche ho jouse hi abolsoh diu ahi, ajeh chu ama hon eisolpa ahet lou jeh u ahi.  
\v 22 Keiman kana seidoh lou hile amaho hi themmo chang pouvinte. Ahinla tun ama hon achonset nau jeh chun thuphat bolthei pouvinte.  
\v 23 Koi hijongleh keima eidoudal'a chun Kapa jong adoudal ding ahi.  
\v 24 Keiman alah uva mi koima dangin abol khah lou thil kabollou hile chonset aneilou dingu ahin; tuvang'in ama hon keima le Ka-Pa kakop lhonin eimu tauvin, ho jong eiho tauve.  
\v 25 Hiche hin Pathen Lekhabuho a kisei, 'Ama hon ajeh beiyin eidoudal ui' kiti chu aguilhun sah ahi.”\x + \xo 15:25 \xt Labu 35:19; 69:4\x*  
\v 26 “Amavang keiman thumopthem–thutah Lhagao, chu kahin sol ding ahi. Pa Pathen a konna hung ding ama chun keima thudol aphondoh ding ahi.  
\v 27 Chule nang hon jong atil'a pat kaumpi jing nahi jeh uva chu kathu hettohsah a napan dingu ahi.”   
\c 16  
\p
\v 1 “Nakipal lhuh louna ding uva thu hicheng hi ka seipeh nahiuve.  
\v 2 Chuleh phat hunglhung ding ahi, kikhopna in'a konna nahin kaidoh dingu, chutengleh koi hileh nathat uva pang hon athil bol'u chu Pathen'a dinga napha tonga kingaito dingu ahi.  
\v 3 Hiche ho jouse hi ipi jeh ham itileh ama hon Pa Pathen ahet lou jeh ule keima eihet theilou jeh u ahije.  
\v 4 Ahinla hiti phat chu ahung lhun tengleh keima tah in kana seipehsa chengse hi na geldoh ding uva thu hicheng hi ka seipeh nahiuve. Chuleh keiman nangho jah a kanasei masah louna ajeh chu phat chomkhat kaumpi ding nahi jeh u ahi.”   
\s1 Lhagao Theng natoh  
\p
\v 5 “Ahinla tua keima eihin solpa henga kile kit ding kahitai, ahin nangho koima chan hoilam a che ding nahim tin jong neidong pouve.  
\v 6 Ahin thu hicheng chu kasei jeh in nalungu lunghem nan adimjo tai.  
\v 7 Ahinla tahbeh a ka seipeh nahiuve, keima ka potdoh chu nangho dinga phatchomna joh ahi, ajeh chu keima kaum laisea nangho kithopi ding chu hung theilou ding ahi. Ahin keima kapotdoh teng, Lhagao Theng chu nangho henga kahin sol ding ahi.  
\v 8 Ama chu ahung tengleh, aman vannoi mite hi chonset thudol, chonphat thudol, chuleh thutan thudol'a ahetphot sah ding ahi.  
\v 9 Chonset thudol chu, ijeh ham itile ama hon keima eitahsan pouve.  
\v 10 Chonphat thenna ho hi chan thei ahi, ijeh inem itile keima Pa kom'a che ding kahi, chuleh nang hon nei mukhah lou diu ahitai.  
\v 11 Chule tun thutanna ahunglhung tai ajeh chu vannoiya vaihompa hi athu tansa a uma ahitai.”  
\v 12 “Chule keiman hiche ho tilouva thil dang tamtah jong ka seipeh nom nahiuve, ahinla nang hon tua nathoh joulou diu ahi.  
\v 13 Lhagao dihtah chu ahung teng vang leh ama chun thutah lam jousea nangho napuihoi dingu ahi, ijeh inem itile aman achama aseilou ding, ajah chan asei ding bou ahi, chuleh khonung thusoh ding na seitoh peh dingu ahi.  
\v 14 Chule ama chun keima eichoiat ding ahi, ajeh chu kanei chengse chu aman alah a nangho na hetsah dingu ahi.  
\v 15 Pa a konna thil jouse chu keima a konna ahisoh keiye, hiche jeh a chu ka phondoh ahi; 'Lhagao Theng chun ana phondoh ho chu aboncha keiya konna alahson ahiye.'”   
\s1 Gimna chu kipana soh ding ahi  
\p
\v 16 “Phat chomkhat jou le nang hon nei mulou dingu ahitai; Ahinla phat chomkhat jouteng neimu kit dingu ahi,” ati.  
\v 17 Hichea chun aseijui ho khat le khat akihouvun, “Chom khat jou le nei mulou dingu, chuleh chom khat jou le neimu kit dingu, ijeh inem itile keima Pa henga che ding kahi, ati hi ipi aseina ahidem? akitiuve.  
\v 18 Chuleh phat chomkhat jou le ati chu ipi aseina ham? Keihon kahe thei pouve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 19 Adoh nom'u chu Jesun ahen ajah uva, “Chomcha khat jou le neimu lou dingu, chomcha khat jou le neimu kit dingu, kati chu itidol ahi khat le khat kidongtoa nahiuvem?  
\v 20 Tahbeh a nangho keima chunga nalhiso diu chule nalungu kham ding ahi; ahinla vannoi mite dinga kipana ahiye, ajeh chu nangho nalungu sangtah a boi ding, ahinla nalung kham nau chu hetman louva kipana thupitah hi ding ahi.  
\v 21 Numei aso dinga anat tengleh athoh gimlheh jin, acha chu asolhah teng vang leh vannoiya mihem khat apen jeh chun akipah jin ahile alungdon hesoh chu aheji tapoi.  
\v 22 Tua nangho nalung lhahdah nau hi, keima in nangho kahin vil kit tengleh thanopna a nadim dingu, chuleh koima chan naguh mangpeh theilou dingu ahitai.  
\v 23 Hiche teng chule nang hon keima imacha neidoh u jong ngai taponte, thutah chu ahile, Pa henga nathum jeng thei u ahitai; ajeh chu keima min'a nathum jeh uva na ngaichat hou chu suh bulhit a um ding ahi.  
\v 24 Chule hiche ho hi masanga nana bolkhah lou u ahiye, Keima min'in thum'un chuteng namu diu ahi, chutengleh kipana sangtah a nanei diu ahi.”   
\s1 Keiman vannoi kajoutai  
\p
\v 25 “Keiman hiche ho jouse hi nangho jah a alem a kasei ahi, ahin phat hunglhung ding chuteng chuleh keiman alema kasei tahlou ding ahi. Ahin Pathen ama hina tah a ka phondoh ding ahi.  
\v 26 Hiche nikho teng chuleh keima min'a nathum dingu keima kanop tah louding ahi ajeh chu keima Pa henga nangho dinga taova kahi,  
\v 27 ijeh inem itile Pa ama tah in nangho na ngailu uve, ijeh inem itile nang hon keima nei ngailu uvin, chuleh keima Pa a konna hung kahi na tahsan tauvin ahi.  
\v 28 Pa kom'a konna vannoiya hung kahin, vannoi ka dalhah a Pa henga chekit ding kahi,” ati.  
\v 29 Hichun aseijui ten adonbut un, “Ven, tun nangin thu alem'a sei talouvin phongtah in naseiye.  
\v 30 Tuhin keihon ima jouse kahe chen tauve. Nangman thil jouse nahesoh hel'in, hiche ho jeh in keihon katahsan tauve; nangma Pathen a konna hung kondon nahi ti katahsan tauve.”  
\v 31 Jesun adong'in, “Achainakeiya neitahsan'u hitam?” ati.  
\v 32 Veuvin, nangho na boncha uva nava cheh sohkei uva keima kachanga nei dalhah dingu phat ahunglhung tai, ahivangin keima kachang kahipoi; ijeh inem itile Pan keima eiumpi nai.  
\v 33 Nanghon kachunga lungmon chamna nanei theina ding uva thu hicheng hi ka seipeh nahiuve, hiche leiset chunga hi nang hon thohgim hahsa tamtah nathoh diu ahiye, ahinla nalungu neosah hih un, ajeh chu lungnom'un, keiman vannoi kajoutai,” ati.   
\c 17  
\s1 Jesu aseijui te dia atao  
\p
\v 1 Jesun thu hicheng chu aseiyin, vanlam aven, “Pa, naphat chu ahung lhunge; Chapan nangma na choiat theina dingin na chapa choian in.  
\v 2 Ajeh chu nangman ama napeh ho jouse chu aboncha aman tonsot hinkemlou apeh dinga, nangman ama chu mijouse chunga thuneina napeh ahi.  
\v 3 Pathen tahbeh khat seh nangman nasol Jesu Christa tah chu ahet doh dingu, hiche hi tonsot hinna ahi.  
\v 4 Chuleh nangman keima bol dinga neipeh chu kajouvin, chule leiset chunga nangma min ka choian tai.  
\v 5 Tun, Pa, vannoi leiset um masanga nangma toh ium laiya iloupina chun nangma tah toh kigomin nei choian in.”  
\v 6 “Vannoi leiset a neina peh ho chu keima in kahin tahlange. Amaho chu nangma a din aum jing uve, chule nangma in keima neipeh ahitan, amaho in nathu chu anit jing nauve.  
\v 7 Tun ama hon nangman keima neipeh thil chengse hi nanga kon ahi ahe tauve.  
\v 8 Hiti ahijeh chun nangman keima neipeh thu ho chu keiman amaho kapen, chule keima hi nanga hung kon kahi jong atahsan tauvin, chuleh nangman neihin sol ahi tijong atahsan tauve.  
\v 9 Chuleh keima amaho dinga katao ahi, vannoi dinga katao ahipoi; Ahin nangman keima neipeh ho dinga bou katao ahi, Ijeh inem itile amaho nanga ahiuve.  
\v 10 Keima'a um jouse nanga ahi, chuleh nangma in keima neina peh ahitai. Ajeh chu ama hon loupina eihin chansah u ahi.  
\v 11 Chuleh keima vannoiya hi kaum louding ahitai, amaho vang hi vannoiya aum nalaiyuve, chule keima nahenga hung ding kahitai. Kapa Theng, eini pumkhat ihi banga amaho jong pumkhat ahi theina dingun, nangman amaho hi vengtup in.  
\v 12 Keima hikom'a kaum sungin, amaho hi kana vengtup e. Amaho hi kaventup jal'in khat cha jong amangthah aum pouve, Pathen Lekhabun anaseisa, manthahna lama chepa tailou chu.”\x + \xo 17:12 \xt Labu 41:9; Jn 13:18\x*  
\v 13 “Chuleh tua keima nangma kom'a hunga kahitai, chule keima leiya kaum laiya chu kipa thanopnaa adim jing theina ding uva kana seipeh sohhel ahitai.  
\v 14 Chuleh keiman nathu amaho kapetai; chule keima vannoiya kahilou banga amaho jong vannoiya ahilou jeh un, vannoi miten aho tauve.  
\v 15 Chule keiman kathum chu amaho hi vannoiya kon'in ladoh in tia katao ahipoi, agiloupa natoh na a kon'in huhdoh in kati joh ahi bouve.  
\v 16 Keima vannoiya konna kahilou banga, amaho jong vannoiya kon ahi pouve.  
\v 17 Chule na thutah chun amaho jouse hi sutheng in ajeh chu nangma thu hi thutah ahiye.  
\v 18 Nangman keima vannoiya neina sol banga chu keiman amaho hi vannoiya kasol ahi.  
\v 19 Chule amaho jouse hi thutah a suhthenga aum theina ding uva amaho jal'a keima kisuthenga kahi.”   
\s1 Jesun tahsan chate jouse dia taona anei  
\p
\v 20 “Keima seijui ho ding seh a tao kahipoi, amaho thuseiya konna keima eitahsan ho jouse dinga jong taova kahi.  
\v 21 Chule amaho chu pumkhat ahina ding uva, Pa, keima nangma sol kahi hi vannoi miten atahsan theina ding uva nangma keiya nauma keima nanga kaum banga hi, amaho jong einia aum theina dinga katao ahi.”  
\v 22 “Keiman amaho chu loupina nangman neipeh ho chu kapetai, amaho eini banga pumkhat ahi theina dingu ahi.  
\v 23 Keima amahoa kauma chule nangma keiya naum, abon'a khat a chamkim soh ahi. Chuteng vannoiyin keima neisol ahi ahet diu chule keima nei ngailut banga hi amaho jong na ngailut ahidan ahetthem diu ahi.  
\v 24 Hepa, nangman neipeh loupina chu nangin neipeh ho hin amu theina dingun, keima umna a chun kakom'a amaho jong umleu kati ahi; chule vannoi bul kiphu masanga nangman nei ngailut ahijeh chun!  
\v 25 “Vo Kapa Theng vannoi leiset miten nangma nahe them thei pouve, ahinla keiman nangma kahen, chule keima neisol hi seijui ho hin ahe tauve.  
\v 26 Keiman nangma hi amaho lah a ka tahlang nahitai, chule keiman hitia chu ka tahlang jing ding nahi; hiche teng chule keima nei ngailutna ho chu amaho'a um ding chuteng keima jong amaho a kaum jing ding ahi.”   
\c 18  
\s1 Jesu kijohdoh chuleh mat a aum  
\p
\v 1 Jesun thu hicheng chu aseiyin apotdoh in Kidron vagal a hon umna a chun aseijui ho toh agalkaiyun, chuin honsunga chun ama le aseijui ho alut tauve.  
\v 2 Jesu pedoh a pang Judas jong chun hilai mun chu ahet chen mama ahi, Ijeh inem itile Pakai Jesun aseijui te chu phat seh a ana pui jing ahi.  
\v 3 Chutah in Judas chun sepaihon chule thempu pipuiho le Pharisee hoa konna sottol leho aloiyin, meivah, meisel, chuleh hem manchah athouvin hiche kom mun chu ahunglhung tauve.  
\v 4 Jesun achunga thil hunglhung ho jouse chu ahesoh keiyin ahi, hichun amaho kom lang chu ajonphei in adongtai, “Koi nahol'u ham?” ati.  
\v 5 Ama hon adonbut un, “Nazareth khoa konna hungkon Jesu chu kahol'u ahi,” atiuvin ahi. Jesun adonbut in, “Ama chu kahi,” ati. (Judas, apedoh a pangpa chu, amaho lah a chu dinga ahi).  
\v 6 Jesun, “Keima hi kahi,” ati chun amaho jouse chu anung chon'un tol'a alhu jengun ahi.  
\v 7 Hichun avel'in adongkit in, “Nanghon koi nahol'u ham?” ati. Chuin ama hon adonbut'un, “Nazareth khoa konna hung Jesu chu kahol'u ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 8 Jesun adonbut in, “Keiman ka seipeh nahiuve, amapa chu keima hi kahi, keima neihol'u ahijeh chun midang ho hi soldoh tauvin,” ati.  
\v 9 “Nangman keima neipeh chengse chu khatcha jong kaman sahpoi, tia asei chu guilhunna dinga chutia ahi.”  
\v 10 Hichun Simon Peter in achemjam asatdoh in Thempu Chungnung sohpa asat le ajetlam abilkol asatlha tai, sohpa min chu Malchus ahi.  
\v 11 Ahinla Jesun Peter jah a, “Na chemjam chu apai sunga koilut kit in, Pan eipeh gentheina khon chu don louva kaum ding ham,” ati.\x + \xo 18:11 \xt Matt 26:39; Mk 14:36; Lk 22:42\x*   
\s1 Thempu Chungnung anga Jesu akailut u  
\p
\v 12 Hichun sepai ho le apipui pau toh chuleh Juda ho sottol lehon Jesu chu aman un akan tauvin ahi.  
\v 13 Annas henga apui masauve; Ijeh inem itile ama chu chuche kuma chu Thempu Chungnung pen'a pang Caiaphas nupa pa ahi.  
\v 14 Hiche Caiaphas hi ahi, “Miho jouse dinga mikhat athi aphajoi,” tia Juda ho ana thumop chu.   
\s1 Peter in Jesu aseilep\x + \xo 18:14 \xt Jn 11:49,50\x*  
\p
\v 15 Simon Peter chun, seijui dang ho bangin, Jesu chu anung ajui tan ahi. Seijui ho lah a khat chu Thempu pipuiho toh ana kihet jeh chun Thempu pipu pa umna gei chu Jesu toh ana lutsah un ahi.  
\v 16 Ahin Peter vang chu polanga phat chomkhat aumin, hichun seijui ho lah a khat thempu pipuipa toh kihepa chun kelkot ngah a pang numeinu kom'a phalna athumin hichun Peter insunga apuilut tai.  
\v 17 Hiche numeinu chun Peter chu thudoh aneiyin, “Nangma hi hiche pa seijui ho khat nahi lou ham? Nangma nahi,” ati. Ahin Peter in adonbut in, “Kahipoi,” ati.  
\v 18 Hiche kom'a chu sohho leh sottol le hon adapjeh a mei akitiuva dinmun'a mei aoiyu ahin, Peter jong adingin mei chu aoiyin ahi.   
\s1 Thempu Chungnung in Jesu thu adoh  
\p
\v 19 Hikom insung langa chun Thempupan Jesu chu thudoh aneiyin, anungjui ho ipi ana seipeh a chuleh ipi ana hilchah em tichu adong tan ahi.  
\v 20 Jesun adonbut in, “Mipi hon ahesoh keiye ipi kana hilchah, chule Hou-In a jong aphat jouse in mipi ho kom'a kana seipeh jinge, guhthima kana seipeh imacha aumpoi.  
\v 21 Ibol'a nangman hiche thudoh ho hi neidoh ham? ka thusei ngai ho le jaho chu nadoh theilou ham? Ajeh chu ama hon ka thuhil jouse chu ahe sohkei uve,” ati.  
\v 22 Hichun Jesun thu hicheng chu aseiyin ahile akom'a Santri ding ho lah a khat in Jesu ngeiphe abengin, “Thempu Chungnung hitia chu kidonbut ngaiyem?” ati.  
\v 23 Hichun Jesun adonbut in, “Keiman kasei khel aum le neimu sah un, ahinla thutah kasei doh jeh a chu ibol'a neivoh uham?” ati.  
\v 24 Hichun Annas chun Jesu chu ahentup in Caiaphas Thempu Chungnung heng lama asoltai.   
\s1 Peter in Jesu aseilep kit  
\p
\v 25 Hiche phat dontah a chu Simon Peter chun dap asah jeh a mei aki oi ahin, ama hon adongkit un, “Nangma hi amaho lah a khat chu nahilou ham?” atiuve. Ahin Peter in adonbut in, “Keima kahipoi,” ati.  
\v 26 Ahinla Thempu Chungnung sohpa Simon Peter in abilkol asatlhah pehpa inko khat in ajah a, “Keiman hon a chu nangma amato kamu nahi lou ham?” atin ahi.  
\v 27 Hichun avel'in Peter in aseilep kit in, chule hetman louvin Ahchal akhong tai.  
\v 28 Chutah chun ama hon Caiaphas in a kon'in gamvaipo pa inlama Jesu akai tauve; hichu jingkah ahina laiye; ahivangin Kalchuh Kut an aneh theina dingun, akisuhboh louna dingun gamvaipo inpia chun amaho alut pouve.  
\v 29 Hichun Pilate apotdoh in, amaho chu aga kimupin thudoh aneiyin, “Hiche pa hin ipi abolkhel atoh khel um hitam?” ati.  
\v 30 Hichun ama hon adonbut un, “Amapa khang-gilou ahilouleh nangma kom'a kahin lhut lou dingu ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 31 Hichun Pilate in adonbut in, “Hiche chu ahitah le, nang hon nungpui tauvin, chuleh nangho dan dungjuijin kitan lhah tauvin,” ati. Hiche phat chun Judah hon adonbut un, “Keima ho Danthu dungjuijin koima thana ding tha kanei pouve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 32 (Hiche hin avetsah chu, Jesun athi ding dan ana seidoh masah chu guilhunna ahi).\x + \xo 18:32 \xt Jn 3:14; 12:32\x*  
\v 33 Hichun Pilate insung dan'ah alut in, Jesu chu akouvin, thudoh aneiyin, “Nangma Juda te lengpa chu nahim?” ati.  
\v 34 Jesun adonbut in, “Hiche thudoh ho hi nangma chama kon ham, ahilou le mi khat touvin keima chung chang n aseipeh ham?” ati.  
\v 35 Hichun Pilate in adonbut kit in, “Kei hi Juda mi kahi ham? Na mite le thempu pipui hon kakhut a eipeh nahi chu, ipi na bolset baham?” ati.  
\v 36 Jesun adonbut in, “Keima Lenggam hi hiche vannoi a kon ahipoi. Hiche vannoi a kon ana hitaleh keima dingin kaseijui hon gal eisat peh intin, Juda te khut a peh doh a kaum louding ahi. Ahinla keima lenggam hi hiche vannoi a kon ahipoi,” ati.  
\v 37 Hichun Pilate in aseikit in, “Ahileh nangma hi lengpa nahim?” atile Jesun adonbut in, “Leng kahi chu nasei khai, Thutah thu hettohsah dinga hung penga, hiche dinga hi vannoiya hunga kahi. Thutah hechan chun thutah ahin photchen diu ahi” ati.  
\v 38 Hichun Pilate in adonbut in, “Thutah chu ipi ham?” Hichun Pilate chu Juda mipi holah a aga potdoh kit in, ajah uva aseitai, “Jesu hi themmona neilou ahi, ati.   
\s1 Jesu tha dia alhuh sah'u  
\p
\v 39 Ahivangin nang hon Kalchuh Kut le mikhat nakilha doh peh dingu chonna ngai khat naneiyui; hijeh chun Juda lengpa hi lhadoh peh leu veng nalungu ham?” ati.  
\v 40 Ahinla ama hon asam'un, “Hiche pa hi hida hen, Barabbas joh,” atin asam tauve. (Barabbas chu doudal natong ahi).   
\c 19  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Pilate in Jesu chu mol'a jep dingin apedoh tai.  
\v 2 Chuin sepai hon ling lukhuh apheh un, Pakai chu akhuh peh tauvin ahi. Chuleh ama hon ponsandup asilpeh un ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin akom'a ahungun, “Juda te lengpa chibai,” atiuvin, totnopnan aneiyun chuleh abengphe abeh peh un ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin Pilate agapot kit in, ajah uva, “Veuvin akhan gitlouna ima kamu lou nahetna ding uva ama naheng uva kahin puidoh ahi,” ati.  
\v 5 Hichun Jesu chu ling lukhuh khuh le ponsandup kisil pum chun ahung potdoh in, chuin Pilate in ajah uva, “Veuvin hiche mipa hi!” ati.  
\v 6 Hichun thempu pipuiho leh Hou-In ngah a pang sepai hon ama chu amu phat un, “Thingpel'a khenbeh-in, thingpel'a khenbeh-in,” tin asam tauve. Ahin Pilate in adonbut in, “Nanghon natahsa tah in kai unlang thingpel'a khenbeh tauvin, keiman vang Jesu hi amona kamu dohpoi,” ati.  
\v 7 Juda te lamkai hon adonbut uvin, “Keiho danpi dungjuiya ama hi athi dinga lomtah ahi, ijeh inem itile ama tah Pathen Chapa akihisah jeh chun,” atiuve.  
\v 8 Hichun Pilate in hiche thu ajah phat in, atil'a sangin akicha cheh tan;  
\v 9 Hichun Pilate chu inpi sunga alut kit in Jesu jah a, “Nangma hoiya hung kon nahim?” ati. Ahivangin Jesun adonbut pon ahi.  
\v 10 Hijeh chun Pilate in ajah a, “Nei houpi louding ham? Nangma lhadohna ding jong chuleh thingpel a khetbehna ding jong thu kanei hi nahet lou ham?” ati.  
\v 11 Hichun Jesun aseitai, “Nangman keima chunga imacha tha nanei na ding aumpoi, amavang chunglam akon tilouvin, ati. Hiti ahijeh a chu keima eipedoh a pangpa chonsetna achungnungpen e,” ati.  
\v 12 Hichun Pilate in Jesu chu lhadoh dingin agong tan, ahinla Judah hon asam uvin, “Nangman hiche pa hi na lhadoh leh Caesar jol nahilou ahi; ama lenga kisem chan chu Caesar douna a thusei ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 13 Pilate in thu chucheng ajah phat chun Jesu chu ahin puidoh in; chuin Pilate chu song lhongnal atiu (Hebrew paova Gabbatha) hichu thutanna a touna chunga chun atou tan ahi.  
\v 14 Hichu Kalchuh Kut dinga kigotni, nidan gup dontah ahi; chuin Juda ho jah a, “Veuvin, na lengpau hi!” ati.  
\v 15 Hijeh chun amaho a-aosot jengun, “Sumangin, sumangin, thingpel'ah khenbeh-in!” atiuvin ahileh, Pilate in ajah uva, “Nalengpau thingpel'a ka khetbeh ding ham?” atileh; thempu pipui hon adonbut un, “Keihon Caesar tailou leng dang kanei pouve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 16 Hichun Pilate in Jesu khetbeh na dingin amaho kom'a apedohtai, hichun Juda ten Jesu chu apuidoh tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Jesu thingpel a akhetbeh u  
\p
\v 17 Hichun ama hon Jesu chu akaiyun, chuin a thingpel akiput in Lugu mun (Hebrew paova Golgotha) atiu mun chu jonin achetan ahi.  
\v 18 Chuleh hiche mun'a chun Pakai Jesu chu thingpel chung'ah akhenbeh tauvin ahi, chuleh midang pasal ni jong asih langto gel'a ama toh akhetbeh thauvin, Jesu chu amani laitah a akikhenbeh un ahi.  
\v 19 Chuin Pilate in thingpel chunga simdoh ding atah in hichu, “Nazareth Jesu, Juda te lengpa,” tin atahdoh in ahi.  
\v 20 Chuleh Jesu akhetbeh na mun chu khopi nai ahijeh chun, hiche min chu Juda ho tamtah-in asimun; hichu Hebrew pao, Latin pao, chuleh Greek paova kisun ahi.  
\v 21 Hichun thempu pipui hon Pilate henga alungkim lounau aga lhut un, hiche kheldohna dingin, “Juda te lengpa” khel'a “Aman aseijin, ‘Keima hi Juda te Lengpa kahi,’” tijoh a khel dingin asei tauve.  
\v 22 Ahin Pilate in adonbut in, “Hithei ponte, ajeh chu keiman kana jihdoh sa chu kajih doh ahitai,” ati.  
\v 23 Chule Rome sepai hon Jesu akhetbeh uchun, aponsil alauvin, hal li asouvin sepai khat hal khat cheh in achang'un; chule asangkhol jong chu alauvin; asangkhol chu khuilou ahin, alua pat ato geiya kikhong lhungkei ahi.  
\v 24 Hichun ama hon aseiyun, “Atel tel'a bokeh sangin leh sangu hitin, vang vetaote, koi chang ding ham” atiuve; hiche hi Pathen thua kijih guilhun na dinga kisei chu ahi. Hichun ama hon von chu alehsang un vangvet nan aneiyun, hiti chun anabol'un ahi.\x + \xo 19:24 \xt Labu 22:18\x*  
\v 25 Hiche jeh chun sepai hon hiti chun hicheng chu abol tauve, Ahin Jesu thingpel kom'a chun anu toh, anu sopinu Mary (Clopas Inneipi) toh, Mary Magdalene ading jingun ahi.  
\v 26 Hichun Jesun anu le angailut aseijui chu akom'a adin amu phat in anu jah a, “Ngailut umtah numei, ven nachapa chu,” ati.  
\v 27 Chuin Jesun hiche aseijui pa jah a aseijin, “Hiche hi nanu ahi,” atin hichun hiche aseijui pa chun Jesu nu Mariam chu a-inlam'a apui tan ahi.   
\s1 Jesu thi  
\p
\v 28 Hiche jou chun Jesun thil ijakai akichai soh chu ahen, Pathen Lekhabua thu chu aguilhun soh thei nan, “Kadang achah e,” ati.\x + \xo 19:28 \xt Labu 69:21; 22:15\x*  
\v 29 Chuleh chukom'a chu belkhat a theitwi thuh kitung ahin, chule twichop phon a theitwi thuh dimset in hyssop molleh a atah un akam toh asuto uvin ahi.  
\v 30 Chuin Jesun theitwi thuh chu adonin, “Akichaitai!” ati. Chuin akaikun alhagao alhadoh tan ahi.   
\s1 Jesu nah tenga asut u  
\p
\v 31 Chuin kiginni ahijeh chun cholngahni a thilong ho chu thingpel'a aumden louna dingin (cholngah ni chula niloupi ni ahin), Judah hon Pilate henga akenggu heboh ding leh along galah mangna dingin athumun ahi.  
\v 32 Hichun Rome sepai ho ahungun mini kikhai Jesu toh kikhenbeh teni keng chu ahehbong tauvin ahi.  
\v 33 Amavang Pakai Jesu kom ahin phah uchun, ama chu ana thitan ahi, hiphat chun Jesu keng vang chu aheh bong tapouve.  
\v 34 Hitia aum vang chun sepai ho khat in Jesu nah chutengcha a asut le apet pet chun thisan le twisih ahung pot tan ahi.  
\v 35 Chule amupa tah chun a hettohsah ahi; chule ama thu hettohsah chu tahbeh ahi; chuleh aman atahbeh asei ahi chu ahei; nang hon jong na tahsan theina dingu ahi.  
\v 36 Hiche ho jouse hi Pathen thua ana kisei doh banga, “Agu khatcha jong kihehbong louding ahi,” ati chu guilhunna dinga thil hicheng chu soh a ahitai.\x + \xo 19:36 \xt Potdohbu 12:46; Minbu 9:12; Labu 34:20\x*  
\v 37 Chule “ama hon tengcha a asutpau chu avet dingu ahi” kiti toh.\x + \xo 19:37 \xt Zechariah 12:10; Rev 1:7\x*   
\s1 Jesu avuiyu  
\p
\v 38 Chuin hicheng jou chun Arimathea Joseph, Jesu seijui khat, amavang Juda ho gin jeh a guhthima hia ahin, ama chun Jesu long chu pohdoh dingin Pilate henga aga thum'in ahileh, Pilate in jong ana phal'e. Hijeh chun ama ahungin Jesu long chu apo mangtai.  
\v 39 Chule Arimathea Joseph toh hung khom pa chu Nicodemus ahin, ama hi Jesu toh kimuto dinga jan muthim'a hungpa chu ahi. Nicodemus chun Myrrh leh Aloes thao namtui kihal, sel som sagi le nga a gih ahin choiyin ahi.\x + \xo 19:39 \xt Jn 3:1,2\x*  
\v 40 Hichun ama hon Jesu long chu alauvin Juda te chonna ngai bangin lounamtui toh tupat ponnemin atom tauvin ahi.  
\v 41 Chuleh thingpel'a aki khetbeh nau mun'a chu hon khat uma ahin, hon a chu koima kivuina khah louhel lhan thah khat uma ahi.  
\v 42 Hijeh chun Juda ho kiginni ahijeh chun lhan chu akomcha ahiman chun chukom'a chun Jesu chu avui tauvin ahi.   
\c 20  
\s1 Jesu thodoh kit  
\p
\v 1 Chuin hapta kipatna nimasani jingkah matah ahunglhung tan, kho jong vah chen loulai ahin, Mary Magdalene chu lhan a chun agachen ahileh song chu lhan a konna tahdohsa aum chu agamui.  
\v 2 Hichun Mary Magdalene chu alhai in Simon Peter leh Pakaiyin angailut seijui pa henga hitin thu aga lhuttai, “Pakai longdamsa chu ama hon apomang tauvin, chule lhan khuh akon'a hoilanga akoiyu ham akihe tapoi” agatin ahi.  
\v 3 Hiche jeh chun Peter le seijui khatpa chu lhan khuh lam jonin ache lhontai.  
\v 4 Hichun seijui teni chu hatah in lhan lam jon'in akilhaitet lhonin ahile seijui khat pa chun Peter akhokhel in lhan khuh apha masa tan ahi.  
\v 5 Ama akunin asung avet le tupat ponnem ho um chu amun, ahivangin asunga alutpoi.  
\v 6 Hichun Simon Peter chu ahunglhung tan, chuin lhan sunga chun alut tai; chuin tupat ponnem ho amu'n chuleh,  
\v 7 aluchunga um ultheh pon chu tupat ponnem ho chutoh umtha louva akijel'a atuma ana um aga mun ahi.  
\v 8 Hichun seijui alhung masajo pa jong chu lhan khuh sunga aga sunglhan, hichu amun atahsan tai.  
\v 9 Hiche masangsea chu ama hon Pathen thu a kiseidoh “Pakai Jesu chu thi ding chuleh hung thoudoh kit ding ahi” tichu ana tahsan theilou u ahi.  
\v 10 Hichun ama hon Inlam ahin jon tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Jesu Mary Magdalene henga akilah  
\p
\v 11 Mary vang chu lhan khuh pam'a chun adingin akap in aka pum chun lhan khuh sung chu aga ven ahi.  
\v 12 Hichun aban a bang vantil ni Jesu long alupsah nauva chu khat alu-lhuna atouva khat akeng todop'a atou amui.  
\v 13 “Ngailut umtah numei nangma ibol'a kap nahim?” tin vantil teni chun ahin dongin ahi. Hichun amanun adonbut in, “Ajeh chu ama hon Ka Pakai apomang tauvin, chuleh alongdamsa chu hoiya akoiyu keiman kahe tapoi,” ati.  
\v 14 Chutia aseijou chun ama akinung heiyin ahileh, Jesu adin amun, ahin Jesu ahi chu ahepoi.  
\v 15 Jesun ahin dong'in, “Ngailut umtah numei, ibol'a kap nahim?” ati. Amanun honlei ngahpa ahisah in, “Pu, hoilaiya nakoi hitam Ka Pakai long chu, nei seipeh in keiman gapomang ing kate,” ati.  
\v 16 “Mary!” tin Jesun ahin koutai. Mary chu Pakai henglam a ahung kihei in akap in, “Rabboni,” ati (hichu Hebrew paova, “houhil,” tina ahi).  
\v 17 Hichun Jesun ajah a, “Nei tongkha hih in; ijeh inem itile keima Pa henga chun kakaltou hih laiye; ahin chen lang kasopi ho jah a gaseiyin, 'Ka-Pa, nangho Pa, Ka Pathen nangho Pathen henga kakal touve,'” ati.  
\v 18 Mary Magdalene chun seijui ho akimupin, hitin aseiye, “Keiman Pakai chu kamutai,” ati. Chuin amanu chun athusei ho chu aseipeh tai.   
\s1 Jesu Aseijui te Henga Akilah  
\p
\v 19 Nikho kipat ni nilhah chun aseijui te Judah ho ginna jeh a kot kikha khuma um ahiuvin, hichun Jesu ahungin amaho lah a ahung dingin ajah uva, “Nachung uva lungmon umhen,” ati.  
\v 20 Aman hiche chu asei jouvin amaho chu akhut thihkil maha le anah tenga kisutna maha avetsah tan ahi. Hichun ama hon Pakai amu u chun seijui te chu akipah lheh jengun ahi.  
\v 21 Hichun Pakaiyin avel'in ahoulimpi kit in, “Nachung uva lungmon umhen, chuleh Pan keima eisol banga nangho kasol nahiuve,” ati.  
\v 22 Hichun Pakaiyin aseijui ho chu ahu ahai khum in, “Lhagao Theng kisan un.  
\v 23 Nanghon koitobang ham khat chu achonsetna na ngaidam uva ahileh kingaidam ahi tauve, ahin nang hon na ngaidam louleh amaho chu kingaidam lou ahi jenge,” ati.\x + \xo 20:23 \xt Matt 16:19; 18:18\x*   
\s1 Thomas tahsan lel  
\p
\v 24 Seijui som le ni ho lah a khat Thomas (Didymus atiu) vang chu Jesu hung kilah a chu amaho lah a ana umlou ahi.  
\v 25 ama hon aseipeh un, “Keihon Pakai chu kamu tauve,” atiuvin ahi. Ahivangin Thomas chun, “Keiman akhut phanga thingkil maha kamua kakhut junga kakhoiya, anah kakhut a katham kahsen keiman tahsan ponge,” ati.  
\v 26 Niget jouvin seijui te insunga aumkhom pettah un, hiche a chu Thomas jong um'ah ahi. Aumnau in chu kot kikhah sohkeiya ahi, hinlah hetmanlou kah in, amasa a bangin, Jesu alah uva ana dingin ahi. “Chamnan nalon khum'u hen,” ati.  
\v 27 Hichun Thomas jah a, “Na khutjung in hinkhoiyin, kakhut teni hi ven; chuleh nakhut hin lhaangin lang kanah tham'in; chuleh gingcha lel tahih in, tahsanin!” ati.  
\v 28 “Ka Pakai le Ka Pathen!” tin Thomas chun ahin phongdoh tai.  
\v 29 Chuin Jesun aseipeh in, “Nangman neimu jeh a nei tahsan ahi. Mulouva tahsan ho anunnomui,” ati.   
\s1 John in hiche lekhabu asutlona  
\p
\v 30 Hiti tah a chu Jesun aseijui te angsunga melchihna kidang tamtah abol ahin, hiti ho chu hiche lekhabu sunga hin akisunlut poi.  
\v 31 Ahinla nang hon Jesu chu Messiah, Pathen Chapa, ahi chu na tahsan uva chule na tahsan vang uva ama min a hinna nanei theina ding uva hichengse hi hiche lekhabua hi kisun'ah ahi bouve.   
\c 21  
\s1 Jesu seijui sagi ho henga akilah  
\p
\v 1 Hichun phat chomkhat jouvin Jesu chu seijui ho toh Galilee dillen panga akimuto kit un, hiti hin ana um'in ahi.  
\v 2 Simon Peter le Thomas (Didymus atiu) chutoh, Galilee gam'a Cana khoa mi Nathanael toh, Zebedee chapa teni toh chuleh seijui dang ni toh umkhom'a ahiuvin;  
\v 3 Simon Peter in, “Keima ngaman in chenge,” ati. Hichun ama hon ajah a, “Keiho jong kahung dingu ahi atiuvin ahi.” Chuin acheuvin kong sung khat ah alut tauve, ahin hiche jan chun imacha aman pouvin ahi.\x + \xo 21:3 \xt Lk 5:5\x*  
\v 4 Jingkah matah in Jesu chu vapam'a adin seijui hon amu uvin, hinlah ama chu koi ahi ageldoh pouve.  
\v 5 Hichun Pakaiyin amaho chu akouvin, “Sopite ho, nga ijat namat tah uvem?” ati. Ahin ama hon adonbut un, “Imacha kaman pouve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 6 Hichun aman, “Nalen'u chu kong jetlam'a gaseplha temun, chule themkhat namat dingu ahi!” ati. Hichun ama hon aseu le nga atam'a tam ahijeh chun akaidoh jou tapouve.\x + \xo 21:6 \xt Lk 5:6\x*  
\v 7 Hichun Jesun angailut seijui chun Peter jah a, “Pakai ahi,” ati. Hichu Peter in Pakai ahi ati chu ajah phat in asangkhol aki-ah loiyin, (asagoh keova um ahin) dillen a chun achom lhan chule vapam lam chu ajon'in ahi.  
\v 8 Adangse vang chu kong sunga atouvun, len chu vapam langa kaidoh ding agong'un, ajeh chu len a chu nga dimset ahin chule amaho vapam alhunna dingu chu tong jani tobang ache beu ngaiyah ahi.  
\v 9 Amaho vapam alhun uchun songmeihol meiya kitih le achunga nga kikoi chuleh changlhah, jing-an a neh ding, amu uvin ahi.  
\v 10 Jesun amaho jah a, “Namatsau nga chu themkhat hinchoiyun,” ati.  
\v 11 Hichun Simon Peter kong sunga alut in len chu vapam langa akaidoh in ngalen jakhat le som nga le thum dimset len chu agakaiyin, nga achuti tam vang chun alen chu a-eh pon ahi.  
\v 12 Hiphat chun Jesun, “Tun nangho hungun lang jing an hung kineh tauvin,” ati. Ahinla aseijui ho lah a chun khatcha beh in jong, “Nang koi nahi ham?” tin adong ngam pouve. Ama hon Pakai ahi chu ahesoh keiyun ahi.  
\v 13 Hichun Pakaiyin seijui ho chu changlhah le nga anehsah in avahva sohkei tai.  
\v 14 Hichu athia konna athodoh nunga aseijui te henga akilah athumvei na ahi.   
\s1 Ka kelngoite vah in  
\p
\v 15 Jing-an anehjou phat'un, Jesun Simon Peter adongin, “John chapa Simon, nangman hiche ho jouse sanga hi nei ngailut joh em?” ati. Peter in adonbut in, henge Pakai keiman kangailut nangman nahe nai.” Jesun ajah a, “Ka kelngoi ho vah in,” ati.  
\v 16 Anivei nan ajah a, “John chapa Simon, nangman nei ngailut em?” atikit tai. Aman ajah a, “Henge Pakai ka-ngailut nangman nahenai,” ati. Hichun Jesun ajah a, “Ka keltah ho chingtup in,” ati.  
\v 17 Jesun athumvei nan adongkit in, “John chapa Simon, nangman nei ngailut em?” ati. Thumvei jen, “Nei ngailut em?” atijeh chun Peter chu alungthim anommo lheh tan, ahin Peter in adonbut in, “Pakai, nangman ijakai nahe sohkeiye, keiman nangma ka ngailutna jouse nangman nahenai,” ati. Hichun Jesun ajah a, “Ka keltah ho vah in,” ati.  
\v 18 “Tahbeh a ka seipeh nahi, na khangdon lai chun nangma deibang tah in navon nakivon theijin, chuleh nangma nop nopna lama nache theiye, ahinla nakum ahungtam tan chujongleh nahung pilhing tan, hijeh a chu nakhut ho nahin jaldoh a midang koi tobangin navon nahin vonpeh ding chuleh nache nom louna lam lama napui dingu ahi,” ati.  
\v 19 Hichu ama iti thia athi ding Pathen achoiat ding chu hetsahna a ati ahi. Chuin hiche chu asei jouvin ajah a, “Kanung hin jui in,” ati.   
\s1 Jesun angailut seijui  
\p
\v 20 Peter akinung heijin avet le anunglam uva–Jesu ngailut seijui, jan anneh pet a Jesu henglam a akingailhua chule “Pakai koiham nangma na pedoh dinga chu,” tia dongpa chu amun ahi.\x + \xo 21:20 \xt Jn 13:25\x*  
\v 21 Peter in Jesu chu thudoh aneiyin, “Pakai hiche pa chula?” ati.  
\v 22 Jesun adonbut in, “Keima kahung kinung lekit kah a anaum dinga phalna kapeh chu, nangma a dinga ipi aboina uma ham? Nangman keima neihin juitan,” ati.  
\v 23 Hichun hiche asei chu, hiche seijui chu thilou ding ahi, tin sopite lah a athang tan ahi; ahinla Jesun ama jah a chu, “Ama chu thilou ding ahi, ati ahipoi. Kahung kahsen umhen, tileng hichu nangman ipi ding natim?” ati ahi bouve.  
\v 24 Hicheng thu hettohsah a chule hicheng thusun a hi hiche seijui chu ahin; ama thu hettohsah chu tahbeh ahi, ti kaheuve.  
\v 25 Chuleh hicheng tailouvin jong Jesun thil kidang tamtah anabol aum'e; hiti ho chu ka geldan in, lekhabun ana kisun sohkei henlang hileh, lekhabua kisun chengse chu vannoi leiset hin dolponte kati.   